<!-- Finding and talking to Gwylan in the shop -->
:: Gwylan Talk Shop
<<effects>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

You search around for Gwylan, following the noise.
<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("talk_intro")>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("talk_intro")>>
	You find <<him>> adjusting the pose of a wooden mannequin. A belted collar hangs from its finger, and a large forest green witch hat sits on its head.
	The hat is adorned with a cluster of flowers and decorated with brown animal ears of some kind.
	<br><br>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("cautious")>>
		"Hello, dear," <<he>> says without turning around. "Is there something you need?"
	<<else>>
		Gwylan finishes posing it, and puts <<his>> hands on <<his>> hips as <<he>> looks it over. <<He>> then turns to you with a smile. "Hello dear, do you need something?"
	<</if>>
<<elseif $gwylan.request.event is "meetAtShop" and !$daily.gwylan.preventProgress>>
	<<if $daily.gwylan.eventCancelled>>
		<<Hes>> still waiting behind the same counter.
	<<else>>
		You find <<him>> waiting behind an old counter.
		<<if Time.season is "winter">>
			<<Hes>> wearing an open-shoulder green tunic under a deep red winter coat.
		<<else>>
			<<Hes>> wearing an open-shoulder green tunic.
		<</if>>
		There's a thick belt around <<his>> waist, bound and tied with all manner of items. A small brown sack tied with some rope, several glass vials tucked into pouches, a small knife in a leather sheath, and various knick-knacks and charms.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $daily.gwylan.eventCancelled>>
		<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
			<<He>> smiles at you. "Come on dear, don't tease me. There's work to be done." <<His>> voice makes you shiver.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> smiles at you. "Are you ready yet?"
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if _gwylanLastSeenDays gte 14>>
			<<He>> looks surprised to see you. "I didn't think you were coming back. It's been weeks! You better have some more stories for me after this. Regardless,
		<<elseif _gwylanLastSeenDays gte 7>>
			"There you are! You kept me waiting for a long time. I was worried that I scared you off for good.
		<<elseif _gwylanLastSeenDays gte 3>>
			"There you are! You're a few days late. I was worried that I scared you off for good.
		<<elseif _gwylanLastSeenDays is 2>>
			"You never showed up yesterday," <<he>> says. "I was worried that I scared you off.
		<<else>>
			"Good timing," <<he>> says. "I'm nearly ready.
		<</if>>
		I'm glad you decided to come."
	<</if>>
<<elseif !$gwylan.request.event and !$gwylanSeen.includes("ritual_beast") and $gwylanSeen.includesAny("caught", "caught_no_lewd")>>
	/* Re-apply meet request if it broke after leaving */
	<<He>> smiles upon seeing you. "Hello, dear. Sorry about the wait, but I'm not quite ready yet. If you could come by <span class="gold">tomorrow</span>, that would be wonderful."
	<<run gwylanRequest("meetAtShop")>><<set $daily.gwylan.preventProgress to true>>
<<elseif $halloween is 1 and !$gwylanSeen.includes("halloween") and $gwylanSeen.includes("hat_found")>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("halloween")>>
	You find <<him>> sat in an old wooden chair with a mushroom-shaped back. <<Hes>> sewing something onto a witch hat. <<He>> looks up and smiles at you.
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("robin_halloween")>>
		"<<if $gwylan.robin gte 10>>Robin<<else>>Your friend<</if>> was so eager to get into the Halloween spirit, it inspired me.
	<<else>>
		"I'm getting into the Halloween spirit.
	<</if>>
	My old hat is getting up there in years, so I'm making a new one." <<He>> holds up <<his>> work for you to see. There's a single fox ear sewn onto it, with another put off to the side, yet to be threaded. They look very realistic.
<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 100 and $gwylan.stage lte 4 and $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
	<<set $gwylan.stage to 5>>
	It seems to be moving around. Whenever you expect to see <<him>> around a corner, there's nothing. You suddenly feel two hands wrap around you from behind. Gwylan's head rests on your shoulder.
	"<span class="green">I can't remember the last time someone was able to find everything the shop has to offer.</span> You must have been through a lot to get to this point. Those who live normal lives don't find much here."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> kisses you on the cheek. "Thank you for everything, dear. You've made an old soul very happy." <<He>> blushes and disengages from you, retreating back behind a counter.
<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 75 and $gwylan.stage lte 3>>
	<<set $gwylan.stage to 4>>
	You find <<him>> tending to some vines hanging from high above. <<He>> turns and smiles at you.
	"You've seen a lot. I can tell by that look in your eyes. <span class="teal">There isn't much left here to escape your notice.</span> Stay strong, and you might just see it all. If that's what you want."
<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 50 and $gwylan.stage lte 2>>
	<<set $gwylan.stage to 3>>
	<<His>> head pops out from behind a large bookcase. <<He>> smiles at you. "<span class="blue">The shop seems to brighten up when you come around.</span> You've been all over, haven't you?"
<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 25 and $gwylan.stage lte 1>>
	<<set $gwylan.stage to 2>>
	You find <<him>> sorting wooden clothing hangars by tree species. "<span class="purple">There's still much to discover,</span> but you're making good progress. Be safe out there."
<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 10 and !$gwylan.stage>>
	<<set $gwylan.stage to 1>>
	You find <<him>> trying to fix an old shelf. It clatters to the ground noisily as you approach. "Find anything you like? I saw your eyes wandering earlier. The more you get around, the more you'll find the shop has to offer."
<<else>>
	<<if !$daily.gwylan.found>>
		<<set $daily.gwylan.found to true>>
		You turn <<print either("a corner", "two corners", "three corners")>> and find <<him>>
		<<cleareventpool>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_find_1">>
			at the end of an aisle,
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_find_2">>
			at an old wooden counter,
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_find_3">>
			between a pair of bookcases,
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_find_4">>
			at the base of a long staircase,
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_find_5">>
			at the <<print either('first', 'second')>> counter to the <<print either('right', 'left')>>,
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<runeventpool>>

		<<cleareventpool>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_1">>
			polishing a mannequin.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_2">>
			brushing <<his>> hair.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_3">>
			sewing patches into a dress.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_4">>
			adjusting the legs of a hat stand.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_5">>
			intently inspecting a ?gwylanItem.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_6">>
			fitting new limbs onto a broken mannequin.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_7">>
			looking at price tags with a confused expression.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_8">>
			tangled up in some surprisingly lively vines. <<He>> manages to shake free just as you approach.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_9">>
			bent over and digging through a large cardboard box. Only <<his>> lower half is visible. <<He>> pulls a ?gwylanItem free from it after a brief struggle.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwy_doing_10" 0.1>>
			moving around various sundries. One slips and lands on <<his>> head, causing <<him>> to let out an involuntary "Bweh!" <<He>> blushes when <<he>> realises that you heard it.
		<</addinlineevent>>
		<<if npcIsPregnant("Gwylan")>>
			<<addinlineevent "gwy_preggers_1" 2>>
				sitting in a rocking chair and knitting what appears to be baby clothes.
			<</addinlineevent>>
			<<addinlineevent "gwy_preggers_2" 2>>
				sitting in a rocking chair and looking at an old doll. It's more stitch than fabric.
			<</addinlineevent>>
			<<addinlineevent "gwy_preggers_3" 2>>
				sitting in a rocking chair with <<his>> eyes closed and <<his>> hand on <<his>> <<bellyDescription 'Gwylan'>>.
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>
		<<runeventpool>>

		<<if $halloween is 1 and $gwylanSeen.includes("halloween") and $gwylanSeen.includes("hat_found")>>
			<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
				<<Hes>> wearing a witch hat with holes for <<his>> fox ears to poke through.
			<<else>>
				<<Hes>> wearing a witch hat adorned with flowers, vines and a pair of <<if _gwylanTF.ears is "fake">>fake <</if>>fox ears.
				<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("hat_colour") and $awarelevel gte 1>>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("hat_colour")>>
					You can't help but notice just how well they match <<his>> hair colour.
				<</if>>
				<<if _gwylanTF.ears is "visible">>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("gwylan_ears")>>
					<span class="pink">You swear that you see one of them twitch.</span>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		You quickly find <<him>> again.
	<</if>>
	<<if Time.isBloodMoon()>>
		<<He>> seems on edge.
	<<else>>
		<<if $gwylanRescue?.failed>>
			<br><br>
			<<gwylanRescueApology "shop">>
		<<else>>
			<<gwylanGreeting>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Talk Tattoos Intro
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("tattoos_intro")>>
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"Y-your tattoos are pretty," you say. "The ones on your tummy."
	<<case "bratty">>
		"You have some pretty intense tattoos on your stomach," you say.
	<<default>>
		"Your tattoos are really neat," you say. "The ones on your stomach."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan blushes and moves <<his>> hands to <<his>> stomach as if to ensure they're not visible.
"Th-thank you. It's a family symbol. Or, rather, it's symbology passed down through my family," <<he>> corrects <<himself>>.
<br><br>

<<He>> takes a moment to compose <<himself>>. You're not sure why such a simple comment took <<him>> off guard.
<br><br>

"It represents the seed of life, and my obligation. It's supposed to help me purify the poison I take in. I've had it for as long as I can remember."
<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
	<<He>> stares off into the gloom.
<<else>>
	<<He>> stares wistfully at the ocean.
<</if>>
<<if $worn.neck.name is "stone pendant" and $gwylanTalked.includes("stone_pendant")>>
	<br><br>
	You break the silence by holding up your stone pendant. "I know we already talked about my pendant, but... the shape's the same. Does that mean it'll help me purify poison too?"
	<br><br>
	Gwylan gives you a wry smile. "I doubt it, dear. That doesn't mean it's not powerful in its own right, though. It's a storied symbol, and it's been around for longer than you or I have been alive." <<He>> touches <<his>> stomach.
<</if>>
"A three-cornered knot with no beginning or end that can never be untied. Part of me is in <<if $location is "forest_shop">>this<<else>>the<</if>> forest, and part of the forest is in me."
<br><br>

<<gwylanOptions>>

:: Gwylan Walk Cafe Solo
<<effects>>
<<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if $phase is 0>>
	<<if $location isnot "forest_shop">><<set $outside to 1>><<set $location to "town">><</if>>
	<<set $daily.gwylan.greeting to true>>
	You nod.
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"That would be really nice."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Sure, that sounds good."
		<<default>>
			"I'd like that."
	<</switch>>
	<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1 or $gwylanSeen.includes("petplay") and $worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
		<<set _magicLeash to true>>
		The thought of being walked by Gwylan makes you blush a little.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	"<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>. Now let's go! I'm starving." You take the route through <<if $bus is "domus">>Barb<<else>>Connudatus<</if>>.
	<br><br>

	<<schoolWalkChat "gwylan">>

	It doesn't take long for you to arrive at the cafe.
	<br><br>

	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_walk")>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe_walk")>>
		"I have a routine, but I can make room in it for you," <<he>> says. "Any day you'd like, <span class="gold">meet me on <<if $bus is "domus">>Domus<<else>>Danube<</if>> Street on any school day after <<ampm 7>>, or at my shop right before then</span>."
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ocean Breeze]]>><<endevent>><<set $location to "cafe">><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"Sorry..." you say, shuffling your feet. "I have other plans this morning. M-maybe tomorrow?"
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Not today," you say. "I've got things to do. Swing by some other day and the answer might change."
		<<default>>
			"I'm afraid I can't," you say. "I have some plans I need to take care of. Another time maybe?"
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan pats your head. "Aww. Very well, I won't force you.<<if $location isnot "forest_shop" and $avery_mansion and ["ascended", "saved"].includes($avery_fate)>>" <<He>> looks around for a moment. <<if $bus is "danube">><<His>> eyes trail up Danube boulevard.<</if>> "Just, stay safe, alright?<</if>>
	Though if you change your mind,
	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_walk")>>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe_walk")>>
		<span class="gold">meet me here after <<ampm 7>>, or at my shop right before then</span>."
	<<else>>
		I'll be there until <<ampm 9 20>>. Feel free to stop by!"
	<</if>>
	<<He>> waves goodbye.
	<br><br>

	<<if $location is "forest_shop">>
		<<link [[Next|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<<elseif $bus is "domus">>
		<<link [[Next|Domus Street]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<<else>>
		<<link [[Next|Danube Street]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Walk Cafe Ask
<<set $location to "town">><<set $outside to 1>><<effects>>
<<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"May I walk to the cafe with you?" you ask.
	<<case "bratty">>
		"Breakfast time?" you ask.
	<<default>>
		"Can I walk to the cafe with you?" you ask.
<</switch>>
<br><br>

<<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1 or $gwylanSeen.includes("petplay") and $worn.neck.type.includes("leash")>>
	<<set _magicLeash to true>>
	You feel a tug on your collar <<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar">>as a glowing leash appears in Gwylan's hand<<else>>and look down to see Gwylan holding your leash<</if>>.
	"Walking <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">> would make my day," <<he>> says with a smile.
	<<if (between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
		"Sadly the cafe's still undergoing renovation. Are you sure you want to just stand around with an old bird like me?" You assure <<him>> that you do. <<He>> smiles. "<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>."
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<if !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30) or $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
		<<He>> smiles. "Of course, dear. I'm just about ready to go."
	<<else>>
		<<He>> looks surprised. "Oh my, but the cafe's still being renovated. Are you sure you want to just stand around with an old bird like me?" You assure <<him>> that you do. <<He>> smiles.
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

You take the route through the park and Starfish Street.
<br><br>

<<schoolWalkChat "gwylan">>

It doesn't take long for you to arrive at the cafe.
<br><br>

<<if !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ocean Breeze]]>><<endevent>><<set $location to "cafe">><<set $daily.gwylan.cafe to true>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<<else>>
	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Cliff]]>><<endevent>><<set $location to "cafe">><<set $daily.gwylan.cafe to true>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<</if>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Walk Cafe Robin
<<set $outside to 1>><<set $location to "town">><<effects>>
<<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _robin to statusCheck("Robin")>>

<<if ["walking_to_cafe", "cafe"].includes(gwylanSchedule())>>
	You leave the orphanage with Robin and wait for Gwylan.
	<br><br>

	Ten minutes go by, and you still see no sign of <<nnpc_him "Gwylan">>.
	<<if C.npc.Gwylan.state === "scorned">>
		You shift uncomfortably, realising <<nnpc_his "Gwylan">> absence is your fault.
	<<else>>
		You're not sure why <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> hasn't shown up. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> always goes to the cafe in the morning.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
		"I don't think <<nnpc_hes "Gwylan">> coming. Maybe it's better if we head to school," you say.
	<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
		"<<nnpc_Hes "Gwylan">> not coming, let's just go before we're late,<<if Weather.temperature gte 30>> I'm melting out here,<<elseif Weather.temperature lte 0>> I'm freezing out here,<</if>>" you say.
	<<else>>
		"I don't think <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">>'ll be here. We should go before we're late for school," you say.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	"Yeah, you're probably right." Robin looks disappointed, but relents.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Go to school (0:20)|Gwylan Walk School Robin]]>><<pass 20>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
<<else>>
	<<npc Gwylan 2>><<person2>>
	<<if Time.minute gte 30>>
		You leave the orphanage with Robin and start to walk to school.
		<br><br>

		"Hey! You two <<if $robinromance is 1>>lovebirds <</if>>weren't about to leave little old me behind, were you?"
		<br><br>

		You both turn around to see Gwylan waving from the opposite sidewalk. <<He>> crosses the street and approaches you both, smiling.
		<br><br>

		"Cafe plans are still a go, right?"
		<br>
		"We didn't think you'd still be waiting for us."
		<br>

		<<if $gwylan.robin gte 50 and $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
			"Oh, nonsense, I'll always make time for my two lushies. Now, let's go already, I'm starving!"
		<<else>>
			"Oh, nonsense, I always make time for friends. Now, let's go already, I'm starving!"
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<if $gwylan.robin gte 20>>
			<<He>> doesn't wait for an answer, marching up to you and taking you and Robin each by a hand.
		<<else>>
			<<He>> doesn't wait for an answer as <<he>> starts walking away. You and Robin share a glance before picking up the pace.
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if $rng gte 51>>
			You leave the orphanage with Robin and see Gwylan already waiting outside.
			<br><br>

			You both walk over and exchange pleasantries before heading to the cafe together.
		<<else>>
			You leave the orphanage with Robin and wait for Gwylan. It doesn't take long for <<him>> to arrive.
			<br><br>

			You both wave <<him>> over and exchange pleasantries before heading out.
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<schoolWalkChat "gwylan" "robin">>

	It doesn't take long before you arrive.
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Gwylan Ocean Breeze]]>><<endevent>><<set $daily.robin_in_cafe to 1>><<set $location to "cafe">><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Walk School Solo
<<set $outside to 1>><<set $location to "town">><<effects>>
<<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if Time.hour is 7 or Time.hour is 8 and Time.minute lt 50>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"Apologies, but would it be alright if we went a little earlier?" you ask. "Please?"
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Hey, we'll be heading to school now. I need to get a leg up on studies," you say.
		<<default>>
			"Could we head to school a bit early?" you ask. "I need some time before class to study."
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	<<if Time.hour is 7>>
		<<He>> checks <<his>> wrist as if <<he>> was wearing a watch. "Already?
		<<if !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
			I've barely had my <<seagullFood>>. Alright, just give me a moment." <<He>> quickly finishes <<his>> food, lightly dabbing <<his>> mouth with a handkerchief when done.
			<<if $rng lte 5>>
				<span class="purple"><<He>> suddenly burps</span>, quickly covering <<his>> mouth in embarrassment. "Oh dear, where are my manners?" <<he>> giggles.
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			Trying to disrupt my routine even more?" <<He>> smiles. "I don't mind.<<if $worn.handheld.type.includes("bookbag")>> Don't forget your bag now!<</if>>"
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<He>> smiles warmly. "No worries, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>. I appreciate the scholarly spirit.<<if $worn.handheld.type.includes("bookbag")>> Don't forget your bag now!<</if>>"
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
	<<He>> stands up with <<his>> plate. <<He>> empties the crumbs into the air, just as a flock of seagulls pass by. They don't let a single crumb land on the beach.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

<<if (Time.hour is 7 or Time.hour is 8 and Time.minute lt 50) and ($worn.neck.name is "familiar collar" and $worn.neck.cursed is 1 or $gwylanSeen.includes("petplay") and $worn.neck.type.includes("leash"))>>
	<<set _magicLeash to true>>
	You feel your collar being tugged on <<if $worn.neck.name is "familiar collar">>as a glowing leash appears in Gwylan's hand<<else>>and look down to see Gwylan holding your leash<</if>>. "Now here comes the highlight of my day," <<he>> begins, pulling you closer until <<his>> hand caresses your cheek. "Walking <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">>."
	<br><br>
<</if>>

You leave the cafe and walk to school.
<<if $rng gte 81>>
	Sam sees you and waves you off.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<schoolWalkChat "gwylan">>

You soon arrive at the front gates.
<<if C.npc.Gwylan.dom gte random(10, 200)>>
	Gwylan suddenly grows a mischievous grin.
	<br><br>

	Just before you walk through, <<he>> takes you by the arm and pulls you into a big hug.
	"Have a good day at school, dear!" <<he>> says far too loudly. Loud enough for several students to turn and look at you.
	<<He>> rubs <<his>> face up against yours and makes a big show of it. <<stress 5>><<gstress>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
		<<He>> finishes it off with an exaggerated kiss to your cheek. "Mwah! Mmmmmwah!" You hear laughter from the other students.
		<<He>> finally releases you, giving you a wink before waving you off.
	<<else>>
		<<He>> releases you after a moment, and winks before waving you off.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<if $cool gte 160>>
		You expect to never hear the end of this as some of your friends approach you. "I thought you lived at the orphanage," one says.
		"I didn't think your <<if $pronoun is "m">>dad<<else>>mum<</if>> would be so hot," another says. "<<He>> doesn't even look the age."
		<br><br>

		You're embarrassed, but at least you're not being made fun of. <<stress 3>><<trauma -2>><<gstress>><<ltrauma>>
	<<else>>
		You can already hear some of the jokes about your '<<father>>' at your expense. <<status -1>><<lcool>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<He>> wishes you a good day at school and waves you goodbye.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|School Front Courtyard]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<br>

