:: Gwylan Ocean Breeze
<<set $outside to 0>><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<if getRobinLocation() is "cafe">><<npc Robin 2>><</if>><<person1>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	The two of you enter the cafe proper. <<if $rng gte 81>>Sam notices and greets you warmly. <</if>>You take a seat at the balcony table<<if $worn.handheld.name isnot "naked">> and put aside your $worn.handheld.name<</if>>.
	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
		The roof of the cafe extends far enough to shield it from the <<print Weather.precipitation>>.
	<</if>>
	Gwylan soon arrives with a plate of <<seagullFood>>.
	<<if $worn.handheld.type.includes("bookbag")>><<set $cafe_study to $worn.handheld.name>><</if>><<handheldundress "cafe_balcony">>
<<elseif $phase is 2>>
	The three of you enter the cafe proper. <<if $rng gte 81>>Sam notices and greets you warmly. <</if>>You and Robin take a seat at the balcony table<<if $worn.handheld.name isnot "naked">>, and you put aside your $worn.handheld.name<</if>>.
	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
		The roof of the cafe extends far enough to shield it from the <<print Weather.precipitation>>.
	<</if>>
	Gwylan soon arrives with a plate of <<seagullFood>>.
	<br><br>

	Robin absentmindedly thumbs through the menu.
	<<if $worn.handheld.type.includes("bookbag")>><<set $cafe_study to $worn.handheld.name>><</if>><<handheldundress "cafe_balcony">>
<<else>>
	당신은 카페의 발코니로 나간다.
	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
		The roof of the cafe extends far enough to shield it from the <<print Weather.precipitation>>.
	<</if>>
	그윌란<<if $phase is 3>>과 로빈은<<else>>은<</if>> 구석진 테이블에 앉아 바다를 바라보고 있다.
	<<if $daily.gwylan_skip_school>>
		An empty plate of sits in front of <<if $phase is 3>>Gwylan<<else>><<him>><</if>>.
	<<elseif Time.hour gte 8>>
		반쯤 먹다 남은 <<seagullFood>> 한 접시가 <<if $phase is 3>>그윌란의<<else>><<him_ yi>><</if>> 앞에 놓여 있다.
	<<else>>
		A plate of <<seagullFood>> sits in front of <<if $phase is 3>>Gwylan<<else>><<him>><</if>>.
	<</if>>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("reunion")>>
		<br><br>
		<<gwylanReunion>>
		<br><br>
		<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("badEndReady") and $phase isnot 3>>
			<<set _noOptions to true>>
			<<He>> doesn't let go. "Please, just let me hold you for a little longer. I really though this would be the end. I thought I'd be alone again."
			<<switch $bodysize>>
				<<case 0 1>><<He>> withdraws only enough to look down into your eyes.
				<<case 2>><<He>> nuzzles <<his>> head into the crook of your neck.
				<<case 3>><<He>> presses <<his>> head into your chest.
			<</switch>>
			"Just a little longer."
			<br><br>

			You feel the slightest pinprick in your arm. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
			<br><br>

			<span class="purple">The balcony starts to shift and distort.</span> Gwylan's face remains in perfect clarity at the centre of your vision. <<He>> smiles sweetly, holding up a pink rose. Its stem drips red. <<hallucinogen 160>><<ggghallucinogens>>
			<br><br>

			You find your legs moving on their own. Gwylan guides you in a dance. "Shhh... just... a little longer."
			<br><br>

			<<hypnosisText "<<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers, and you're no longer where you once were.">> <<His>> voice fades away with the rest of the cafe.
			<br><br>

			<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
				<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Nowhere Passout]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
			<<else>>
				<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Taken Start]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
		<<else>>
			<<He>> holds you for just a moment longer, before letting go and returning to <<his>> seat. <<He>> motions to a free seat opposite <<him>>.
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("cafe")>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe")>>
				"Would you like to join <<if $phase is 3>>us<<else>>me<</if>>? I come here every morning to clear my head. Maybe it'll help for you, too."
			<<elseif $gwylan.hunting is 3>>
				"Take a seat. My eyes have missed looking at you. <<gwylanCommand "You'll be coming by the shop later, too.">> We have some catching up to do."
			<<elseif _badEndFollowup>>
				"The shop must have something new to show you after going through that. Be sure to take a look around later, and we can talk more. Until then, would you like to join <<if $phase is 3>>us<<else>>me<</if>>? A bit of fresh ocean air might be just what you need to clear your head."
			<<else>>
				"Would you like to join <<if $phase is 3>>us<<else>>me<</if>>? A bit of fresh ocean air might be just what you need to clear your head."
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("cafe")>>
		<br><br>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe")>>
		<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
			"Y-you look lonely," you say. "Do you mind if I sit?"
		<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
			"You look like you could use some company," you say. "I hope this seat isn't taken."
		<<else>>
			"여기 앉아도 괜찮나요?" 당신은 묻는다. "외로워 보이는데."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		그윌란이 놀란 눈으로 당신을 바라본다.
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("chef_chat")>>
			"You've already used that line on me,"
		<<else>>
			"여기 사람들 대부분은 나를 신경쓰지 않는데 말이지. 가끔은 내가 투명인간인 것 같다니까,"
		<</if>>
		그가 키득거리며 말한다. 커다란 갈매기가 발코니에 내려와 그를 향해 고개를 갸웃거린다.
		그가 음식 부스러기를 던지자, 갈매기는 그것을 입에 물고 날아간다.
		<br><br>

		"그래, 앉아도 돼," 마침내 그가 말한다.
		<<if $worn.handheld.type.includes("bookbag")>><<set $cafe_study to $worn.handheld.name>><</if>><<handheldundress "cafe_balcony">>
	<<else>>
		<<if $gwylanRescue?.failed>>
			<br><br>
			<<gwylanRescueApology>>
		<<else>>
			<<gwylanGreeting>>
		<</if>>
		<<if $worn.handheld.type.includes("bookbag")>><<set $cafe_study to $worn.handheld.name>><</if>><<handheldundress "cafe_balcony">>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if !_noOptions>>
	<<gwylanOptions>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Cliff
<<set $outside to 0>><<set $location to "cafe">><<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
<<if $phase is 1>>
	You and Gwylan head over to the railing down the road from the cafe.
	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
		<<He>> unfolds a large dark green umbrella and starts watching the sea. There's plenty of room under it for you.
	<<else>>
		<<He>> leans against it and starts watching the sea.
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	You approach Gwylan.
	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
		<<Hes>> holding a large dark green umbrella, and watching the sea.
	<<else>>
		<<Hes>> leaning against a railing and watching the sea.
	<</if>>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("reunion")>>
