		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
			<<He>> notices you out of the corner of <<his>> eye. Before you can blink, you are wrapped up in <<his>> warm embrace. <<if _gwylanTF.known>><<His>> tail curls around you. It's very soft.<</if>>
			<br><br>

			"Oh, sweetheart," <<he>> whispers. "You've been gone so long, I was starting to think you were never coming back. What happened to you?"
		<<else>>
			<<He>> notices you out of the corner of <<his>> eye. <<He>> smiles widely. "There you are!" <<He>> walks up and hugs you. "I was starting to wonder if you had forgotten about me. What happened to you?"
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
		<<gwylanReunion>>
		<br><br>

		<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("badEndReady")>>
			<<set _noOptions to true>>
			<<He>> doesn't let go.
			<br><br>

			"Please, just let me hold you for a little longer. I really though this would be the end. I thought I'd be alone again."
			<<switch $bodysize>>
				<<case 0 1>><<He>> withdraws only enough to look down into your eyes.
				<<case 2>><<He>> nuzzles <<his>> head into the crook of your neck.
				<<case 3>><<He>> presses <<his>> head into your chest.
			<</switch>>
			"Just a little longer."
			<br><br>

			You feel the slightest pinprick in your arm. <<pain 2>><<gpain>>
			<br><br>

			<span class="purple">The street starts to shift and distort.</span> Gwylan's face remains in perfect clarity at the centre of your vision. <<He>> smiles sweetly, holding up a pink rose. Its stem drips red. <<hallucinogen 160>><<ggghallucinogens>>
			<br><br>

			You find your legs moving on their own. Gwylan guides you in a dance. "Shhh... just... a little longer."
			<br><br>

			<<hypnosisText "<<He>> snaps <<his>> fingers, and you're no longer where you once were.">> <<His>> voice fades away with the rest of the town.
			<br><br>

			<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("aurigaScarConfront")>>
				<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Nowhere Passout]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
			<<else>>
				<<link [[Everything fades to black...|Forest Shop Taken Start]]>><<pass 1 hour>><<endevent>><</link>>
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<He>> holds you for just a moment longer, before letting go.
			<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("cafe")>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe")>>
				"Would you like to join me? I come to the cafe every morning to clear my head. Maybe it'll help for you, too."
			<<elseif $gwylan.hunting is 3>>
				"Take a seat. My eyes have missed looking at you. <<gwylanCommand "You'll be coming by the shop later, too.">> We have some catching up to do."
			<<elseif _badEndFollowup>>
				"The shop must have something new to show you after going through that. Be sure to take a look around later, and we can talk more. Until then, would you like to join me? A bit of fresh ocean air might be just what you need to clear your head."
			<<else>>
				"Would you like to join me? A bit of fresh ocean air might be just what you need to clear your head."
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
	<<elseif !$gwylanSeen.includes("cafe")>>
		<br><br>
		<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe")>>
		<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
			"Y-you look lonely," you say. "Do you mind if I join you?"
		<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
			"You look like you could use some company," you say. "I hope there's room for me."
		<<else>>
			"Do you mind if I join you?" you ask. "You look lonely."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		Gwylan looks to you with surprise.
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("chef_chat")>>
			"You've already used that line on me,"
		<<else>>
			"Most don't pay me any mind here. Sometimes I think I'm invisible,"
		<</if>>
		<<he>> says with a giggle. A large seagull lands on the railing, and tilts its head at <<him>>. <<He>> flicks a bread crumb at it, which it catches in its mouth before flying off.
		<br><br>

		"I wouldn't mind the company," <<he>> finally says.
	<<else>>
		<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none">>
			There's plenty of room under <<his>> umbrella for you.
		<</if>>
		<<if $gwylanRescue?.failed>>
			<br><br>
			<<gwylanRescueApology>>
		<<else>>
			<<gwylanGreeting>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>
<br><br>

