:: Gwylan Ocean Breeze Watch
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _robin to statusCheck("Robin")>><<set _robinPresent to $location is "cafe" and $daily.robin_in_cafe is 1>><<silently>><<seagullFood>><</silently>>
<<if $phase2 is 1>>
	<<switch $phase>>
		<<case "fruity ale">>
			<<wearProp "fruity ale">><<set _food to "a fruity ale. It arrives quickly, served in a regular beer glass. It's very sweet and light. It's delicious">>
		<<case "winter ale">>
			<<wearProp "winter ale">><<set _food to "winter ale. It arrives promptly, served in a beautifully curved glass. It's sweet, rather than bitter. It's delicious">>
		<<case "shandy">>
			<<wearProp "shandy">><<set _food to "a shandy. It arrives quickly. It's served in a can with a beer glass; you're clearly meant to pour it yourself. It's lemon flavoured and very refreshing">>
		<<case "autumn ale">>
			<<wearProp "autumn ale">><<set _food to "an autumn ale. It arrives quickly. It's sweet and has a hint of caramel. It's delicious">>
		<<case "coffee">>
			<<wearProp "coffee">><<set _food to "a cup of coffee. It's strong, but not too strong">>
		<<case "milkshake">>
			<<wearProp "milkshake">><<set _food to "a milkshake, with two straws. It's very sweet">>
		<<case "fruit salad">>
			<<wearProp "salad fork">><<set _food to "a fruit salad. It arrives promptly, full of fresh strawberries, blueberries, kiwi, and chunks of pineapple. It's sweet and delicious">>
		<<case "gingerbread">>
			<<wearProp "gingerbread">><<set _food to "a gingerbread man. It arrives promptly, a friendly icing face smiling up at you. It's sweet and delicious, and <<print $christmas is 1 and Time.monthDay is 25 ? `it's the perfect treat for Christmas Day` : `it reminds you of Christmas`>>">>
		<<case "pancakes">>
			<<wearProp "pancake fork">><<set _food to "a stack of freshly made pancakes. It arrives promptly, topped with a large helping of butter and jam. The smell is delicious, and has a hint of vanilla">>
		<<case "crepes">>
			<<wearProp "pancake fork">><<set _food to "a plate of crepes. It arrives quickly, filled with strawberries and topped with a light sprinkle of powdered sugar. It's very sweet">>
		<<case "deluxe cream bun">>
			<<wearProp "cream buns">><<set _food to "one of the cafe's staple cream buns. It soon arrives, fresh from the oven and filled to the brim with creamy goodness. The flavour is divine">>
		<<default>>
			<<wearProp "fork">><<set _food to "the food. It arrives promptly, and it's delicious">>
	<</switch>>
	You order _food.
<</if>>

당신은 그윌란<<if _robinPresent>>, 로빈<</if>>과 함께 바다를 바라보며 <<print Weather.precipitation is "rain" ? "entranced by the rain and the waves" : Weather.isSnow ? "entranced as snowflakes vanish into the waves" : "산들바람을 즐긴다">>.
<br><br>

<<if $gwylan.request.event is "meetAtCafe">>
	/* Story progress, unlock intro for second ritual */
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("struggles")>><<gwylanRequestEnd "skip">>
	<<if _robinPresent>>
		"Robin, would you be a dear and give me and your <<if $robinromance>><<girl>><</if>>friend a moment to ourselves?" Gwylan says. "There's a personal matter I need to discuss with <<phim>> is all."
		<br><br>

		<<if Time.schoolDay>>
			<<He>> smiles. "We'll meet you outside afterwards. Don't forget your backpack, now."
		<<else>>
			<<He>> pulls out some cash, and hands it to Robin. "Here, go and order yourself something nice in the meantime, so the staff don't give you any trouble."
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		Robin does a quick <<if _robin.pronoun is "m">>bow<<else>>curtsy<</if>> and exits the balcony. Gwylan turns <<his>> attention back to you.
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
	"내가 반드시 알아야 할 것이 있다고 했었지," 그가 말한다. "알아야겠어. 넌 이미 내게 많은 이야기를 해 줬지만, 나는..."
	<br><br>

	그는 시선을 돌려 다시 바다를 바라본다. "나는 욕심이 많아. 네가 무언가를 말해줄 때마다, 더 알고 싶어져. 이제는 무언가가 나를 갉아먹는 것처럼 느껴질 정도야. 알아야 할 것이 있어. 그 어느 때보다 더."
	그는 당신을 돌아보며, 음울하면서도 매혹적인 표정을 짓는다.
	<br><br>

	"어떻게 그 모든 걸 버틸 수 있는 거야? 네가 내게 들려준 것들을 다른 이들이 듣는다면, 모두가 무너질 거야.<br>
	<span class="gold">
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("likes_tentacles")>>The tentacles that have violated you so much that you're now accustomed to them.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("kylar_kidnapped")>>
		카일라, 너를 납치하고 강제로 결혼하려던 소년.<br>
	<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("kylar_parents")>>
		카일라, 너를 납치했다던 소년.<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("farm_defended")>>The way you defended your farm from Remy, without giving so much as an inch.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("tenyclus")>>The gaps in your memory after you played that strange game too much.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("christmas_generosity")>>How you were so desperate for money that you resorted to stealing, and yet, when you found someone in more need than you, you left a large sum of money for them instead.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("underground_brothel")>>Your escape from sex slavery.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("underground_farm")>>The human cattle farm.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("eden_known")>>Your time with the hunter, and your efforts to smother <<nnpc_his "Eden">> loneliness.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("likes_wolves")>>Your integration into the local wolf pack.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("bird")>>Your time in the old castle with the hawk.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("prison")>>Your confinement in prison.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("asylum")>>Your treatments in the asylum.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("temple_confessor")>>The terrible truth told to you by the bishop.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("temple_exorcist")>>The way you rescued someone from a dark ritual while working a dance job.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("temple_sexy")>>The burdens of the world you've taken on while trying to purge its poisons.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("historic")>>The stories and history you've sought out.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("hookah")>>The terrible things you've seen, and how you inherited the hookah parlour.<br><</if>>
	<<if $chef_speech is "bailey">>How you bravely told everyone about what Bailey is doing at the orphanage during the cafe's grand re-opening.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("islander")>>Your exile to the island, and everything you've told me about the culture you found there.<br><</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("fox_mask")>>How you accompanied an Elk to the Rite of Renewal as a Fox.<br><</if>>
	<<if $brownFoxRevealed>>
		<<if $avery_mansion?.heist_suspicion isnot undefined>>
			How we stole the clutching bones together.<br>
		<<elseif $avery_mansion?.fox.stones>>
			How you boldly stole the clutching bones from Avery.<br>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("auriga_scar")>>
		The Elk's wound over your heart.<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $gwylanTalked.includes("succubus")>>
		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("fall_from_grace")>>
			Your fall from grace.
		<<else>>
			Your personal march through Hell.
		<</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	네가 다시는 내게 돌아오지 않을까 봐, 다시는 이야기해주지 않을까 봐 전부를 외웠어."
	</span>
	<br><br>

	그의 눈이 무언가를 찾듯 위에서 아래로 당신을 바라본다. "하지만, 너는 돌아왔어. 어떤 고난이나 성취를 마주해도 너는 계속 돌아와. 무엇이 네가 희망을 버리는 걸 막는 거야?"
	<br><br>

	당신은 오랫동안 생각하며, 지금까지 겪은 모든 일을 떠올린다.
	<br><br>

	무엇보다도, 당신을 살아가게 하는 것은...
	<br>
	<<link [[Spite|Gwylan Talk Struggles Spite]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Survival instinct|Gwylan Talk Struggles Survival]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Thoughts of a better future|Gwylan Talk Struggles Optimism]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if Object.values(V.children).length>>
		<<if Object.values(V.children).length is 1>>
			<<link [[Your child|Gwylan Talk Struggles Children]]>><</link>>
		<<else>>
			<<link [[Your children|Gwylan Talk Struggles Children]]>><</link>>
		<</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[The other orphans|Gwylan Talk Struggles Orphans]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if $fame.good gte 400>>
		<<link [[The need to help others|Gwylan Talk Struggles Kind]]>><</link>><<note "Kindness fame" "green">>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Someone important to you|Gwylan Talk Struggles Special]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<if displayDefiantOption(850) or $sadism_level gte 2>>
		<<link [[Revenge|Gwylan Talk Struggles Revenge]]>><<if $submissive gt 850 and $wolfgirl gte 6>><<wolfDefiant 850>><</if>><</link>><<if displayDefiantOption(850)>><<defianttext 850>><<else>><<note "Sadist" "lewd">><</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $angel gte 6 or $fallenangel gte 2 or ["monk","priest"].includes($temple_rank)>>
		<<link [[Divine purpose|Gwylan Talk Struggles Divine]]>><</link>><<if $angel gte 6>><<angel>><<elseif $fallenangel gte 2>><<fallenangel>><<else>><<note "Temple rank" "gold">><</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $demon gte 6 or $backgroundTraits.includes("lustful") or $auriga_scar>>
		<<link [[Lust|Gwylan Talk Struggles Lust]]>><</link>><<if $demon gte 6>><<demon>><<elseif $auriga_scar>><<note "Elk-scarred" "red">><<else>><<note "Lustful" "lewd">><</if>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<if $innocencestate is 1>>
		<<link [[Say you don't know what <<he>> means|Gwylan Talk Struggles Innocent]]>><</link>><<note "Innocent" "teal">>
		<br>
	<<elseif $awarelevel gte 4 or $temple_confessor_intro or $hookah_state gte 2 or $auriga_scar>>
		<<link [[The need to find answers|Gwylan Talk Struggles Answers]]>><</link>>
		<br>
	<</if>>
	<<link [[Say you don't know|Gwylan Talk Struggles Unknown]]>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<link [[Say you don't want to keep going|Gwylan Talk Struggles Desolate]]>><</link>>
	<br>
<<else>>
	<<if $phase2 is 1>>
		<<switch $phase>>
			<<case "fruity ale">>
				<<wearProp "fruity ale">>
			<<case "winter ale">>
				<<wearProp "winter ale">>
			<<case "shandy">>
				<<wearProp "shandy">>
			<<case "autumn ale">>
				<<wearProp "autumn ale">>
			<<case "coffee">>
				<<wearProp "coffee">>
			<<case "milkshake">>
				<<wearProp "milkshake">>
			<<case "fruit salad">>
				<<wearProp "salad fork">>
			<<case "gingerbread">>
				<<wearProp "gingerbread">>
			<<case "pancakes">>
			<<case "crepes">>
				<<wearProp "pancake fork">>
			<<case "deluxe cream bun">>
				<<wearProp "cream buns">>
			<<default>>
				<<wearProp "fork">>
		<</switch>>
		Gwylan briefly looks over at your $phase.
		<<switch $phase>>
			<<case "coffee">>
				"Are you drinking that for flavour, or to wake up? It doesn't do anything for me unless I add a bunch of my own brew to it."
			<<case "fruity ale" "shandy" "autumn ale" "winter ale">>
				"Getting started early, are we?"
				<<if $stress gte ($stressmax / 5) * 3 or $trauma gte ($traumamax / 5) * 2>>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bad_day_drinking")>>
					<<He>> looks concerned. "No judgement, but you should only drink to make a good day better. No offense either, but you look troubled as it is."
				<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 50>>
					<<if npcIsPregnant("Gwylan")>>
						<<He>> pouts. "So rude to drink in front of me right now." <<He>> gently rubs <<his>> <<bellyDescription "Gwylan">>.
					<<else>>
						<<He>> thinks for a moment, before shrugging. "Why not? I'll cheer with you." <<He>> orders a $phase too<<if _robinPresent and !npcIsPregnant("Robin")>>, and another one for Robin<<set $daily.robin_cafe_food to 1>><</if>>. You clink your drinks together.
						<<if $islander_language gte 100>>
							<<He>> cheers in the islander's tongue.
						<<else>>
							<<He>> says something in a language you don't recognise, but it sounds like a cheer.
						<</if>>
					<</if>>
				<<else>>
					<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bad_day_drinking")>>
					<<He>> giggles. "You should only drink to make a good day better, so I hope your day's already going well."
				<</if>>
			<<case "milkshake">>
				<<He>> notices that there's two straws sticking out.
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("romance")>>
					"You're such a sap." <<He>> smiles. "It's okay. I like it." You enjoy the milkshake together.
				<<else>>
					"Really? Trying to buy my affections now?" <<He>> laughs. "You're lucky you're cute."
				<</if>>
			<<case "pancakes">>
				"Pancakes and crepes are very similar. The difference is that crepes don't use a leavening agent and are usually served with fruit. Overseas, pancakes are made much thicker. In fact, almost every country has a different kind of pancake."
				<<if Time.season isnot "winter">>
					<<He>> takes a bite of <<his>> crepes. "These are still my favourite."
				<</if>>
				<<if _robinPresent>>
					<br><br>
					Robin seems deep in thought. "I wish I could travel overseas someday. Heck, I'd take anywhere that isn't this dump of a town..." <<person2>><<He>> catches <<himself>>. "Um, n-not that I don't enjoy your company! I'd take you with me as well. The other orphans too if I could."<<person1>>
				<</if>>
			<<case "crepes">>
				<<if Time.season is "winter">>
					"I do like my crepes, but I can't eat it every day for a year straight. I need a break during the colder months."
				<<else>>
					"Ooh, little copycat," Gwylan says with a giggle. "Sammy likes to mix up the fruit the crepes get served with. <<nnpc_He "Sam">> tries to judge how the person ordering it is feeling that day, and picks a fruit to match."
				<</if>>
			<<case "gingerbread">>
				"There's a strange joy in eating a food that's shaped like people, isn't there?"
				<br><br>

				Gwylan looks at you with a serious glare, but cracks a smile and starts laughing. "I'm just kidding."
			<<default>>
				"Good choice."
		<</switch>>
		<br><br>
	<<elseif $phase2 is 2>>
		<<switch $phase>>
			<<case "fruity ale">>
				<<wearProp "fruity ale">>
			<<case "winter ale">>
				<<wearProp "winter ale">>
			<<case "shandy">>
				<<wearProp "shandy">>
			<<case "autumn ale">>
				<<wearProp "autumn ale">>
			<<case "coffee">>
				<<wearProp "coffee">>
			<<case "milkshake">>
				<<wearProp "milkshake">>
			<<case "fruit salad">>
				<<wearProp "salad fork">>
			<<case "gingerbread">>
				<<wearProp "gingerbread">>
			<<case "pancakes">>
			<<case "crepes">>
				<<wearProp "pancake fork">>
			<<case "deluxe cream bun">>
				<<wearProp "cream buns">>
			<<default>>
				<<wearProp "fork">>
		<</switch>>
		<<print either("Fishing", "Rummaging", "Searching", "Shuffling", "Sorting", "Digging")>> through your $cafe_study, you pull out your textbook on $phase. You spend some time going through the material.
		The <<if Weather.precipitation is "rain">>pouring rain makes<<else>>crashing waves make<</if>> for some pretty calming background noise for studying.
		<br><br>

		Gwylan watches idly as you flip through the pages<<if _gwylanTF.known>>, <<his>> large tail slowly swishing behind <<him>><</if>>.

		<<if $rng lte 20>>
			<br><br>
			You get stuck on one particular part. Despite re-reading it over and over, the information just doesn't seem to want to stick.
			<br><br>

			Gwylan picks up on it and asks what you're having difficulties with. You show <<him>> the page you're on. <<He>> grabs the book and quickly skims through it.
			<br><br>

			After a brief minute <<he>> hands it back to you, and guides you through each part, while still allowing you to reach the answers on your own. After some time, you feel that you can finally grasp the topic.

			<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
				You lean over and plant a kiss on <<his>> cheek in gratitude. <<He>> puts a hand over the spot and smiles bashfully.
			<<else>>
				You thank <<him>> for the help. <<He>> leans back and tips <<his>> hat in response.
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			You manage to absorb the information in the chapter without too much effort, and bookmark where you left off for later.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>

	/* Robin arrives here if the player went to the cafe early. */
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_walk_robin") and $robin.timer.hurt is 0 and !$daily.robin_in_cafe and $robinmissing is 0 and !$robinlocationoverride and Time.schoolDay and Time.hour gte 8 and false>> /* WARNING! Re-enable later for Gwybin cafe */
		<<set $daily.robin_in_cafe to 1>><<set _robin to statusCheck("Robin")>><<set _robinPresent to true>><<npc Robin 2>><<person2>>
		The door to the cafe proper opens, and Robin steps out onto the balcony.

		<<if false>> /* If Robin hasn't seen PC in a long time */
			<br><br>
			<<His>> jaw drops when <<he>> sees you. You have no time to react as you're quickly tackled into a hug.
			<br><br>

			<<His>> face buries into your shoulder as <<he>> starts spouting mostly incomprehensible gibberish. You are able to decipher some of it. <span class="green">It's about how much <<hes>> missed you.</span> <<trauma -6>><<ltrauma>>
			<br><br>

			<<He>> eventually pulls apart and wipes <<his>> tears. But <<his>> expression soon turns serious. "So, if you're here, why haven't you come to see me yet? I've been worried sick," <<he>> says. You struggle to come up with an answer. "Nevermind, it doesn't matter anymore. I'm just glad you're safe. <<if $robinromance>>I love you.<</if>>"
			<br><br>

			<<He>> composes <<himself>>, and smiles at you. Gwylan smiles too. "You have a very loyal friend, <<pcpetname "Gwylan">>. Be sure to take care of <<him>> like <<he>> takes care of you."
		<<elseif _robin.trauma gte 80>>
			<<He>> doesn't say a word as <<he>> sits down, slumped forward and expressionless.
			<br><br>

			You and Gwylan share a worried look, but don't press <<him>> on the matter.
		<<elseif _robin.dom gte 60 and _robin.trauma lt 40>>
			<<He>> waves at Gwylan and turns to you.
			<br><br>

			"I figured you'd be here! Mind if I join you?" <<He>> moseys over to the empty seat.
			<<if $phase2 is 1>>
				<<He>> notices your order. "$phase.toUpperFirst(), huh? Smells <<if !["fruity ale", "shandy", "autumn ale", "winter ale"].includes($phase)>>real good<<else>>interesting<</if>>."
			<<elseif $phase2 is 2>>
				<<He>> notices the $phase textbook in front of you. "Getting a head start on studying? Smart." <<He>> pulls out <<his>> own $phase textbook and starts leisurely browsing through some of the chapters.
			<</if>>
		<<else>> /* Expand this whole section depending on Robin's and the player's state */
			<<He>> waves at Gwylan and turns to you.
			<br><br>

			"Ah, there you are! I thought you may have gone to school early." <<He>> takes the empty seat.
			<<if $phase2 is 1>>
				<<He>> notices your order. "Ooh, you got $phase? Smells<<if !["fruity ale", "shandy", "autumn ale", "winter ale"].includes($phase)>> lovely<<else>>... quite strong<</if>>."
			<<elseif $phase2 is 2>>
				<<He>> notices the $phase textbook in front of you. "Good idea. I've got a bit to catch up on myself, actually." <<He>> pulls out <<his>> own $phase textbook and flips to one of the later chapters, going quiet as <<he>> focuses on the material.
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
		<<person1>>
	<</if>>

	You enjoy the view in silence for a while.
	<br><br>

	<<cleareventpool>>

	<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
		<<if _robinPresent>> /* Robin-exclusive events */
			<<if $phase2 is 1 and !$daily.robin_cafe_food>>
				<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_robin_hungry" 1>>
					<<set $daily.robin_cafe_food to 1>><<set _noOptions to true>><<set _wouldBuy to ($robinmoney + (_robin.dom * 2) + ($robinpaid is 1 ? 200 : 0)) / 10 gte random(0, 100)>><<generateRole 2 0 "waiter/waitress">><<person2>>
					You're halfway through your $phase when you hear Robin's stomach rumble.
					<<switch $phase>>
						<<case "coffee">>
							<<if $robinmoney gte 2 and _wouldBuy>>
