							<<if $robinmoney gte 10 and _wouldBuy>>
								<<set _isBuying to true>><<set _foodCost to 10>>
								<<He>> considers the idea for a moment, before waving to get the attention of the <<person3>><<person>> nearby.
							<<else>>
