							<<link [[Buy Robin a Deluxe Cream Bun (£50)|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Robin Buy]]>>
								<<if $phase is "deluxe cream bun">><<npcincr Robin dom 1>><</if>><<npcincr Robin love 2>>
								<<set $phase to "deluxe cream bun">><<set $phase2 to 2>><<money -5000 "cafe">>
							<</link>><<gglove "Robin">><<if $phase is "deluxe cream bun">><<gdom "Robin">><</if>>
							<br>
						<</if>>
						<<if ["winter ale", "fruity ale", "shandy", "autumn ale"].includes($phase) and npcIsPregnant("Robin")>>
							<span class="blue">You decide against sharing your $phase with <<him>>, knowing <<hes>> with child.</span>
							<br>
						<<else>>
							<<skinicon "give">>
							<<link [[Share the rest of your $phase with <<him>>|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Robin Buy]]>>
								<<set $phase2 to 3>><<stress 8>><<npcincr Robin dom 1>><<npcincr Robin love 1>>
							<</link>><<gstress>><<glove "Robin">><<gdom "Robin">>
							<br>
						<</if>>
						<<refuseicon>>
						<<link [[Ignore <<him>>|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Watch]]>>
							<<set $phase2 to 0>><<npcincr Robin dom -2>>
						<</link>><<ldom "Robin">>
						<br><br>
					<</if>>
				<</addinlineevent>>
			<</if>>

			<<if _robin.crossdressing gte 2 and _robin.crossdressing lte 4 and _robin.dom lt 80 and !$weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_robin_cd>>
				<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_robin_crossdressing" 1>>
					<<set $weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_robin_cd to 1>>
					Robin awkwardly adjusts <<person2>><<if Time.schoolDay>>the waistband of <<his>> school <<if $pronoun is "m">>skirt<<else>>shorts<</if>><<else>><<his>> <<npcClothesText _robin "upper">><</if>>. <<His>> attempts to be subtle clearly didn't work, as Gwylan quickly perks up.
					<br><br>

					"That fits you really well, you know?"
					<br><br>

					Robin shifts around some more, then pauses, realising the comment was for <<him>>. "Oh! Hah... I'm glad you think so," <<he>> says, looking down sheepishly.
					<br><br>

					Gwylan pouts a little, and leans in. "Look at me." Robin looks <<person1>><<him>> in the eyes. "You look gorgeous, so why do you look so ashamed?"
					<br><br>

					Robin appears at a loss for words for a moment, but <<his>> expression soon changes into that of a big smile. <<npcincr Robin dom 3>><<gwylanRobin>><<ggdom "Robin">>
					<br><br>
				<</addinlineevent>>
			<</if>>
		<</if>>

		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_feed" 1>>
			Gwylan takes a piece of <<seagullFood>><<if _seagullFood isnot "gingerbread">> in <<his>> fork<</if>>, and holds it out over the edge of the balcony. Immediately, a gull swoops by and eats it right off of <<if _seagullFood isnot "gingerbread">>the fork<<else>><<his>> palm<</if>> without stopping.
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>

		<<if _seagullFood is "cherry crepes">>
			<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_cherry" 1>>
				"Watch this." Gwylan impales a cherry on <<his>> fork and eats it, stem and all.
				<<He>> chews for a few moments, before sticking <<his>> tongue out, revealing <span class="lewd">nothing but the stem, tied in a nearly perfect knot</span>.
				<br><br>

				<<if _robinPresent>>
					<<person2>>Robin's eyes quickly dart away as <<his>> cheeks flush.<<person1>>
					<br><br>
				<</if>>

				<<He>> spits it off to the side, where it's caught by a passing gull. <<He>> winks at you. <<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><<glust>>
				<br><br>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_chef_truth") or $chef_speech is "truth">>
			<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_cream_buns" 1>>
				"You've ruined these cream buns for me, you know?"
				<br><br>

				<<He>> quickly realises how that sounds, backpedaling. "By that, I mean the normal buns. Your special ones were already tastier, and then I found out how they were made? Honestly, how could I go back?"
				<br><br>

				<<if _robinPresent>>
					Robin looks at both of you, expecting either of you to elaborate. You and Gwylan simply share a look, and giggle.
					<br><br>

					<<person2>><<He>> pouts and crosses <<his>> arms. "Hey, what's with the big secret? You can tell me too!"
					<br><br>

					<<He>> soon gives up when it becomes clear neither of you are going to give a straight answer.<<person1>>
					<br><br>
				<</if>>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>
	<<else>>
		<<if ($chef_rework lte 0 or $chef_state is 8) and !$weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_cafe_opening>>
			<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_cafe_opening" 10>>
				<<set $weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_cafe_opening to true>>
				<<He>> looks over in the direction of the newly renovated cafe.
				<br><br>

				"The place is coming along nicely. Sammy always has been an ambitious one." <<He>> turns to you. "Thank you for making <<nnpc_his "Sam">> ambitions a reality."
				<br><br>

				There's a brief silence before <<he>> continues. "Me personally, I can't wait to finally have my routine back. It may have been monotone, but I've really missed it.<<if $gwylan.sea gte 20>> Well, monotone without you that is.<</if>>"
				<br><br>

				Another silence. "...Anyway, you better get going with the opening ceremony soon so I can get back to having my <<seagullFood>>!" <<he>> quips, gently punching your shoulder. "I'll be in attendance, so be sure to look out for me."
				<br><br>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<if !$weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_ice_cream and _robinPresent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_event_ice_cream" 1>>
			<<set _noOptions to true>>
			<<set $weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_ice_cream to true>><<if random(1, 2) is 1>><<generateNPC 2 t m m>><<else>><<generateNPC 2 t f f>><</if>><<person2>>
			You see a child <<print either("walking", "running", "gently humming", "spinning around")>>
			<<if $location is "cafe">>
				on the walkway below,
			<<else>>
				on the walkway nearby,
			<</if>>
			holding an ice cream cone. <<He>> trips and <span class="red">drops it onto the pavement</span>. <<He>> lowers <<his>> head, and you hear <<him>> begin to cry. Gwylan makes a small noise from beside you. <<person1>><<He>> rushes away from the <<if !between(V.chef_state, 7, 8)>>balcony<<else>>railing<</if>>.
			<br><br>
			<<if inappropriatePlayerState("clothes")>>
				<span class="blue">You don't think you should follow <<him>> in this state of dress.</span>
			<<elseif inappropriatePlayerState("bodywriting")>>
				<span class="blue">You don't think you should follow <<him>> while covered in lewd bodywriting.</span>
			<<elseif inappropriatePlayerState("fluids")>>
				<span class="blue">You don't think you should follow <<him>> while covered in lewd fluids.</span>
			<<elseif inappropriatePlayerState("drugs")>>
				<span class="blue">You don't think you should follow <<him>> while intoxicated.</span>
			<<else>>
				<<link [[Follow|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Ice Cream]]>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>>
			<</if>>
			<br>
			<<link [[Watch|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Ice Cream]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
			<br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_ocean_floor" 1>>
		"Strange to think that there are things on the ocean floor older than humans<<if _robinPresent>>," Gwylan says.<<else>>."<</if>>
		<br><br>

		You're not sure how to respond.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_shore_tide" 1>>
		"The tide comes and goes without thought of the shore." <<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<He>><</if>> places <<his>> hands on the railing. "Sometimes I feel like the shore, and other times I feel like the tide."
		<br><br>

		<<if isLoveInterest("Gwylan")>>
			You place your hand on <<hers>>.
			<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
				"The shore can be patient," you say. "It will wait for the tides as long as the tides let it."
			<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
				"The tides may go, but they always come back." You give <<his>> hand a squeeze. "I know you'll come back."
			<<else>>
				"Tides ebb and flow," you say. "The shore just has to wait."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>

		<<He>> smiles at you, though it's tinged with sadness. You turn to watch the ocean again.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_salty" 1>>
		"I've always loved the salty air near the beach. Makes me feel alive<<if _robinPresent>>," Gwylan says.<<else>>."<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_fins" 1>>
		"We emerged from the deep parts of the sea on fins, and now we rule the earth. You can do anything you put your mind to, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">><<if _robinPresent>>," Gwylan says.<<else>>."<</if>>
		<br><br>

		It's a comforting thought.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_drowning" 1>>
		"Did you know that drowning is painful right up until you let the water into your lungs? Then it's peaceful." <<stress 3>><<gstress>><<if _robinPresent>><<npcincr Robin trauma 1>><<grtrauma>><</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_chips" 1>>
		You point out a flock of seagulls harrying a tourist for some chips. Gwylan giggles. It's a nice sound.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_swimming" 1>>
		You ask if Gwylan has ever swam in the ocean. <<He>> looks away from you.
		<br><br>

		"I'm afraid if I do, I'll enjoy it too much."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> doesn't say anything else.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_couple" 1>>
		A couple stop and kiss by the edge of the water. They're in complete bliss. Gwylan looks wistful as <<he>> watches.
		<br><br>

		<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>
			<<if _robinPresent>>
				<<set _noOptions to true>>
				Your eyes wander to Gwylan's lips, looking dreadfully unkissed. However, <span class="lewd">Robin's right there</span>. You consider your options.
				<br><br>

				<<link [[Kiss Gwylan|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Kiss]]>><<set $phase to 0>><</link>><<kissvirginitywarning>>
				<br>
				<<if $robinromance is 1>>
					<<link [[Kiss Robin|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Kiss]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>><<kissvirginitywarning>>
					<br>
				<</if>>
				<<link [[Keep watching the couple|Gwylan Ocean Breeze Kiss]]>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
			<<else>>
				You lean forwards and kiss <<him>>. <<He>> smiles against your lips before kissing back. You only break apart to breathe. <<gwylanKiss>><<takeKissVirginity "Gwylan" `(isLoveInterest("Gwylan") ? "loveInterest" : "romantic")`>>
				<br><br>
			<</if>>
		<<elseif $loveInterest.primary isnot "None">>
			<<if $player.virginity.kiss === true>>
				You find yourself wondering what a kiss like that must feel like.
			<<elseif $loveInterest.primary is "Black Wolf">>
				Your mind drifts to the Black Wolf's <<if $blackwolfmonster is 1>>lips on yours<<else>>wet tongue licking your face<</if>>.
			<<elseif $loveInterest.primary is "Great Hawk">>
				Your mind drifts to the Great Hawk's <<if $greathawkmonster is 1>>lips on yours<<else>>beak gently preening you<</if>>.
			<<else>>
				Your mind drifts to <<= $loveInterest.primary>>'s lips on yours.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_gulls" 1>>
		"I like listening to the seagulls. They have a lot to say, if you care enough to hear<<if _robinPresent>>," Gwylan says.<<else>>."<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_nature" 1>>
		A fish jumps out of the water into the waiting talons of a bird. It flops a few times before going still. "Nature is brutal. That makes it beautiful, though, in its own way<<if _robinPresent>>," Gwylan says.<<else>>."<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<if _gwylanStatus.includes("dom") or $gwylanSeen.includes("dog_bowl")>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_scratch" 1>>
			<<set _tf to checkTFparts()>>
			<<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<He>><</if>> reaches over and scratches behind your ears. "<<pcPetname "Gwylan" "good">>."
			<br><br>

			You feel warm and a little aroused. <<arousal 900>><<garousal>>
			<<if _robinPresent>>
				<<npcincr Robin dom -1>><<ldom "Robin">>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_bump_shoulder" 1>>
		You playfully bump your shoulder against <<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan's<<else>><<hers>><</if>>. After a moment, <<he>> returns the gesture.
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<if !$weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_business>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_business" 1>>
			<<set $weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_business to 1>>
			You ask about the shop. Gwylan is happy enough to chat about it. Seems as though business
			<<if _gwylanLovePercent gte 100>>
				couldn't be better.
			<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 75>>
				is going well.
			<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 50>>
				is looking up.
			<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 25>>
				is slow.
			<<else>>
				is non-existent.
			<</if>>
			<<if _robinPresent>>
				<<if _gwylanLovePercent gte 100>>
					Robin smiles, and asks a few questions <<person2>><<himself>>.
				<<elseif _gwylanLovePercent gte 50>>
					Robin smiles.
				<<else>>
					Robin offers <<him>> a sympathetic smile.
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<if $trauma gte ($traumamax / 5) * 3>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_trauma" 1>>
			"Are you taking care of yourself?" <<if _robinPresent>><<he>><<else>>Gwylan<</if>> asks. "If you can't sleep, come by the shop sometime. I'm sure it has something for you."
			<br><br>

			<<if _robinPresent and C.npc.Robin.trauma lt 80>>
				Robin puts a hand on your shoulder. "I'm here for you too. Always."
				<br><br>
			<</if>>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_whale" 1>>
		"At night, I can hear whales singing all the way from my little shop," <<he>> says. "They sound so lonely. I wish I could sing back to them."
		<br><br>

		<<if _robinPresent>>
			"Really?" Robin asks. "That's so cool!
			<<if C.npc.Robin.trauma lt 20>>
				Maybe I should leave my window open tonight so I can hear them too."
			<<else>>
				I love the sound of whales. It helps me relax."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_skateboard" 1>>
		A <<personsimple>> on a skateboard crashes. <<He>> gets up and looks around to see you<<if _robinPresent>>, Robin<</if>> and Gwylan staring down at <<him>>. Looking embarrassed, <<he>> continues on. You both giggle. <<stress -4>><<lstress>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_wind" 1>>
		The wind pulls at Gwylan's hat. <<He>> places a hand on it to keep it from blowing away. You think about how much it suits <<him>> and say as such. <<He>> smiles, blushing a little. <<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><<glust>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_peaceful" 1>>
		<<if _robinPresent>>
			There are no words passing between you three, yet you feel at peace. You can tell that they feel the same. <<stress -6>><<npcincr Robin trauma -1>><<lstress>><<lrtrauma>>
		<<else>>
			There are no words passing between you two, yet you feel at peace. You can tell that Gwylan feels the same. <<stress -6>><<lstress>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<if (Time.monthDay is Time.lastDayOfMonth or Time.isBloodMoon(Time.date)) and ($avery_tower?.progress is undefined or $avery_tower?.progress lt 100) and $world_corruption_hard gt 0 and $world_corruption_soft gt 99>>
		<<if $hallucinations gte 2>>
			<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_nobody" .33>>
				<<set $daily.gwylan.noTalk to true>><<gwylanNobody 1>>
				<<set _noOptions to true>>
				You realise quickly that <<he>> seems more translucent than usual.
				<br><br>

				"<span class="witch-gone">I'm sorry,</span>" <<he>> says. <<His>> voice is hard to remember. "<span class="witch-gone">I'm not quite feeling myself today.</span>"
				<br><br>

				<<if _robinPresent>>
					<<set _noOptions to true>>
					<<person2>>Robin <<if C.npc.Robin.dom gte 80>>snaps <<his>> fingers<<else>>waves <<his>> hand<</if>> in front of your face. "Hellooo? Come on, we're going to be late for school if we don't go now."
					<br><br>

					Was that Robin's voice you heard earlier? Besides <<him>>, nobody's here.
					<br><br>
					<<awareness -10>><<trauma 9>><<lawareness>><<gtrauma>>
					<br><br>

					<<schoolicon "building">><<link [[Walk to school (0:10)|Gwylan Walk School Robin]]>><<pass 10>><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
					<br>
					<<getouticon>><<link [[Excuse yourself and go back inside (0:01)|Ocean Breeze]]>><<pass 1>><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><<endevent>><</link>>
					<br>
				<<else>>
					You wonder who said that. You're the only one on the balcony, after all. Nobody is around.
					<br><br>

					<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
						<<getouticon>><<link [[Go back inside (0:01)|Ocean Breeze]]>><<pass 1>><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><<endevent>><</link>>
					<<elseif $location is "cafe">>
						<<getouticon>><<link [[Leave (0:01)|Cliff Street]]>><<pass 1>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
					<</if>>
					<br>
				<</if>>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<<else>>
			<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_blood_moon" .33>>
				<<set $daily.gwylan.noTalk to true>><<gwylanNobody 1>>
				<<set _noOptions to true>>
				<<He>> looks up at the sky. "The end of the month fills me with restless anticipation," <<he>> says. "It must be something in the water. The moon controls the tides, and the tides control me."
				<br><br>

				You look at <<him>>. <<He>> smiles, as if to reassure you. It feels hollow. Like if you looked too close, you'd fall into an endless void. <<stress 9>><<gstress>>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> turns back to the ocean. "I'm sorry, dear. I'm not feeling myself today. Come back tomorrow."
				<br><br>

				You make your exit. /* Robin variation here */
				<br><br>

				<<if $location is "cafe" and !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
					<<getouticon>><<link [[Go back inside (0:01)|Ocean Breeze]]>><<pass 1>><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><<endevent>><</link>>
				<<elseif $location is "cafe">>
					<<getouticon>><<link [[Leave (0:01)|Cliff Street]]>><<pass 1>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
				<</if>>
			<</addinlineevent>>
		<</if>>
	<</if>>

	<<if Weather.precipitation isnot "none" and !$daily.gwylan_sea_talk_weather>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_weather" 1>>
			<<set $daily.gwylan_sea_talk_weather to 1>>
			<<if Weather.precipitation is "rain">>
				"Do you like getting caught in the rain?" <<he>> asks.
				<br><br>

				<<if $uncomfortable.nude is true>>
					<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
						"I try not to get wet if I can avoid it," you admit. "People stare at me... and it makes me uncomfortable."
					<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
						"People always stare at my <<chestsimple>> when my clothes get wet," you say. "I try not to get wet anymore."
					<<else>>
						"Not if I can help it," you say. "People like to stare."
					<</if>>
				<<else>>
					You blush.
					<<if $speech_attitude is "meek">>
						"Well... the rain is a good excuse to 'accidentally' show off," you say.
					<<elseif $speech_attitude is "bratty">>
						"It's a real dopamine rush, not knowing if I'll find cover in time," you say.
					<<else>>
						"I don't mind getting a bit wet, if that's what you're asking," you say.
					<</if>>
				<</if>>
				<br><br>

				<<He>> nods. "I love it. I'll sleep <<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>><span class="lewd">naked</span> <</if>>in my garden whenever it rains. I feel nourished."
				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners") and false>> /* Re-enable this when the ability to go to Gwylan's garden is added */
					<<He>> pauses, <<his>> cheeks dusting pink. "If you want, you can stop by next time it's raining." <<npcincr Gwylan lust 1>><<glust>>
				<<else>>
					<<He>> smiles at you. "You should try it sometime."
				<</if>>
			<<elseif Weather.precipitation is "snow">>
				"I love this weather," <<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<he>><</if>> says. "There's something so satisfying about jumping into a snowbank. Like a blanket of cold. Did you ever do anything fun in the snow?"
				<br><br>

				You<<if _robinPresent>> and Robin<</if>> talk about all the snowball fights you had <<if _robinPresent>>together as children<<else>>as a child<</if>> before Bailey broke them up. Gwylan listens with a small smile.
				When you finish, <<he>> makes <<if _robinPresent>>three snowballs and hands one to each of you<<else>>two snowballs and hands one to you<</if>>. "Aim for that lamp post," <<he>> says. "First one to hit it wins."
				<br><br>

				<<if $rng lte 5>>
					<<generate3>>
					<span class="pink"><<if _robinPresent>><<print either("You accidentally hit", "Gwylan accidentally hits", "Robin accidentally hits")>><<else>><<print either("You accidentally hit", "Gwylan accidentally hits")>><</if>> a <<person3>><<person>> instead.</span> <<He>> yelps as cold snow soaks into <<his>> jacket.
					<<if _robinPresent>>
						The three of you duck under the railing before <<he>> sees you. You all giggle together. <<trauma -3>><<npcincr Robin trauma -1>><<ltrauma>><<lrtrauma>>
					<<else>>
						You both duck under the railing before <<he>> sees you. You both giggle. <<trauma -3>><<ltrauma>>
					<</if>>
				<<elseif random(-200, 1200) lt $athletics>>
					<span class="green">You manage to hit it first.</span> Gwylan leans forward and <<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>kisses you on the cheek<<else>>gives you a hug<</if>>. <<trauma -3>><<ltrauma>><<if _robinPresent and $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>><<npcincr Robin dom -2>><<ldom "Robin">><</if>>
				<<elseif _robinPresent and $rng lte 50>>
					<span class="teal">Robin hits it first.</span> You <<person2>><<if $robinromance is 1>>lean forward and kiss <<him>> on the cheek<<else>>cheer for <<him>><</if>>. <<trauma -3>><<npcincr Robin love 1>><<ltrauma>><<glove "Robin" "simple">>
				<<else>>
					<span class="teal">Gwylan hits it first.</span> You <<if $gwylanSeen.includes("partners")>>lean forward and kiss <<him>> on the cheek<<else>><<if _robinPresent>>and Robin <</if>>cheer for <<him>><</if>>. <<trauma -3>><<ltrauma>>
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				"How peculiar, I've never encountered this type of weather before," <<he>> says.
				<br><br>

				You look up, and see a large hole in the sky. <span class="red">Something's not right.</span> You feel that you should report this to a meteorologist, or somebody who can identify this phenomena, so it can be talked about with Gwylan.
				<br><br>

				...In case it wasn't obvious already, this is a bug. <span class="teal">Please report.</span>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_dog" 1>>
		<<endevent>>
		<<beastNEWinit 1 dog>><<npc Gwylan 2>><<person2>>
		<<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<He>><</if>> leans further out over the balcony. There's a <<beasttype 0>> biting at the leaves blowing in the wind. You smile at the sight. Gwylan smiles too.<<if _robinPresent>> Robin awws.<</if>> <<stress -4>><<lstress>><<if _robinPresent>><<npcincr Robin trauma -1>><<lrtrauma>><</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<if $chef_state>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_sam" 1>>
			<<npc Sam 3>>
			You hear some footsteps behind you. Sam comes <<if !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>out onto the balcony<<else>>over and rests a hand on the railing<</if>>. <<person3>><<He>> smiles at you<<if _robinPresent>> and Robin<</if>> before turning to Gwylan.
			<<if !(between($chef_state, 7, 8) and $chef_rework lte 30)>>
				"Everything okay up here? Do you need anything?"
				<br><br>

				"Everything's fine," Gwylan says. <<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>><<person1>><<He>> takes your hand. <</if>>"Thank you for letting us up here, Sammy."<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>> <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" `(V.gwylanSeen.includes("partners") ? "romantic" : "consensual")`>><</if>>
				<br><br>

				"Any time!" Sam beams. "Gwylan is my best customer," <<person3>><<he>> tells you. <span class="lewd">"Always buying cream buns."</span>
				<br><br>

				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_chef_truth") or $chef_speech is "truth">>Gwylan blushes and avoids looking at you.<<else>>Gwylan shrugs.<</if>> "What can I say? They're delicious."
				<br><br>

				"Next one is on the house," Sam says. <<He>> waves goodbye. Gwylan sighs.
				<br><br>

				"<<Hes>> such a sweetheart," <<person1>><<he>> says. <<person3>><<if $chef_state gte 9>>"I'm glad you helped <<him>> so much. The cafe is everything to <<him>>."<<else>>"<<He>> loves this cafe and wants to see it expand. I hope <<he>> can one day."<</if>>
			<<else>>
				"Everything okay out here?"
				<br><br>

				"Everything's fine," Gwylan says. <<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>><<person1>><<He>> takes your hand. <</if>>"I'm just missing my routine."<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>> <<takeHandholdingVirginity "Gwylan" `(V.gwylanSeen.includes("partners") ? "romantic" : "consensual")`>><</if>>
				<br><br>

				"It won't be long! The renovations will be done before we know it," Sam beams. "Gwylan is my best customer," <<person3>><<he>> tells you. <span class="lewd">"Always buying cream buns."</span>
				<br><br>

				<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_chef_truth") or $chef_speech is "truth">>Gwylan blushes and avoids looking at you.<<else>>Gwylan shrugs.<</if>> "What can I say? They're delicious."
				<br><br>

				"When we re-open, first ones are on the house," Sam says. <<He>> waves goodbye. Gwylan sighs.
				<br><br>

				"<<Hes>> such a sweetheart," <<person1>><<he>> says. <<person3>> "I'm glad you're helping <<him>> so much. The cafe is everything to <<him>>."
			<</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_sneeze" 1>>
		<<if _robinPresent>>
			<<if $rng gt 66>>
				Gwylan sneezes. The sudden noise makes you and Robin jump. Despite the surprise, it sounded cute.
			<<elseif $rng gt 33>>
				Robin sneezes. The sudden noise makes you jump. Gwylan reaches into <<his>> pocket and pulls out a handkerchief. <<He>> wipes Robin's nose before <<person2>><<he>> has a chance to.
			<<else>>
				You sneeze. Gwylan reaches into <<his>> pocket and pulls out a handkerchief. <<He>> wipes your nose before you have a chance to.
			<</if>>
		<<else>>
			<<if $rng gte 51>>
				<<He>> sneezes. The sudden noise makes you jump. Despite the surprise, it sounded cute.
			<<else>>
				You sneeze. <<He>> reaches into <<his>> pocket and pulls out a handkerchief. <<He>> wipes your nose before you have a chance to.
			<</if>>
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_bird_yip" 1>>
		A bird lands right in front of <<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<him>><</if>>.<<if _gwylanTF.known and !_robinPresent>> <<His>> tail pops out and swishes.<</if>> <<He>> leans forwards until <<his>> hat threatens to fall off.
		<br><br>

		<<if $fox gte 6>>
			You yip at it.
			<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
				Gwylan yips too.
				<<if _robinPresent>>
					Robin looks bemused.
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			Startled, it flies away.
		<<else>>
			After watching it for a minute, it flies away.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_world" 1>>
		"Be careful out there," Gwylan says. "It's a dangerous world we live in."
		<br><br>

		<<if $trauma gte ($traumamax / 5) * 3>>
			You let your thoughts turn to the abuse you've suffered, and shiver.
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
		<<if _robinPresent and C.npc.Robin.trauma gte 80>>
			<<person2>>Robin fidgets in <<his>> seat.
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<if !$gwylanSeen.includes("horse_fingers")>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_horse" 1>>
			<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("horse_fingers")>>
			"Horses run on bones not unlike our fingers," Gwylan says out of the blue. "That's why they can paw at the ground when they count."
			<br><br>

			<<He>> demonstrates using <<his>> pointer. You <<if $tending gte 400>>knew that already, but <<if _robinPresent>>Robin looks fascinated<<else>>enjoy the demonstration nonetheless<</if>>.<<else>>find it hard to believe, but trust that Gwylan must be right.<<if _robinPresent>> Robin looks fascinated.<</if>> <<tending 10>><<gtending>><</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_song" 1>>
		<<if $seabird_lullaby gte 2>>
			<<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<He>><</if>> begins to hum <span class="teal">Seabird's Lullaby</span>. You join in with <<if $harpy gte 6>>your clear, beautiful voice<<else>>your best efforts to follow along<</if>>. You think <<hes>> happy for the company.
		<<else>>
			<<if _robinPresent>>Gwylan<<else>><<He>><</if>> begins to hum a <span class="teal">faintly familiar melody</span>.
		<</if>>
		<br><br>

		<<if _robinPresent>>
			<<person2>>Robin closes <<his>> eyes and listens intently. <<His>> shoulders start to relax. <<if $seabird_lullaby gte 2 and $harpy gte 6>><<npcincr Robin trauma -2>><<llrtrauma>><<else>><<npcincr Robin trauma -1>><<lrtrauma>><</if>>
			<br><br>
		<</if>>
	<</addinlineevent>>

	<<if $gwylan.robin gte 1 and !$weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_robin and !_robinPresent>>
		<<addinlineevent "gwylan_watch_sea_robin" 1>>
			<<set $weekly.gwylan_sea_talk_robin to 1>>
			<<if $gwylan.robin gte 10 or $gwylanSeen.includesAny("robin_cafe", "robin_cafe_trauma")>>
				"How's Robin doing?" <<he>> asks.
			<<else>>
				"How is your friend doing?" <<he>> asks. "Robin, right?" <<He>> smiles at you.
			<</if>>
			"You should bring <<nnpc_him "Robin">> to the shop <<if $gwylan.robinShop>>again<<else>>sometime<</if>>. I have plenty of outfits that would look good on <<nnpc_him "Robin">>."
			<br><br>
		<</addinlineevent>>
	<</if>>

	<<runeventpool>>

	<<if !$daily.gwylan.sea>>
		<<set $daily.gwylan.sea to true>>
		<<set $gwylan.sea++>>
	<</if>>
	<<if !_noOptions>>
		<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
		<<if _robinPresent>><<npc Robin 2>><<person1>><</if>>
		<<gwylanOptions>>
	<</if>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Ocean Breeze Robin Buy
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>><<set _robin to statusCheck("Robin")>>
<<if $phase2 is 2 or $phase2 is 5 or $phase2 is 7>> /* Buy */
	<<if $phase2 is 2>> /* Robin did nothing */
		You signal for a <<person3>><<person>>.
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"Hi... Err, could we have- um, order, some $phase please? F-for my friend, if it's not too much trouble?" you ask.
			<<case "bratty">>
				"Put in an order of $phase for my friend here, and make it snappy," you say.
			<<default>>
				"I'd like to order some $phase, thank you. It's for my friend," you say.
		<</switch>>
		You hand over the money. The <<personsimple>> nods and disappears into the cafe.
		<br><br>

		<<person2>>Robin smiles. "That's really sweet of you."
	<<elseif $phase2 is 5>> /* Robin tried to pay */
		The <<person3>><<person>> quickly arrives at your table. "May I be of service?"
		<br><br>

		"Yes, I would like the $phase, thank you," Robin says. <<person2>><<He>> reaches into <<his>> wallet to pay, but you put your hand on <<hers>>. "I'll cover it." You pay the <<person3>><<personsimple>>.
		<br><br>

		Robin smiles and <<if $robinromance>>kisses you on the cheek<<else>>pulls you into a one-armed hug<</if>>.
	<<else>> /* Robin paid */
		The <<person3>><<person>> quickly arrives at your table. "May I be of service?"
		<br><br>

		"Yes, I would like the $phase, thank you," Robin says, holding out a banknote. "Certainly, it'll be just a moment." The <<personsimple>> disappears into the cafe.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<person2>>
	<<switch $phase>>
		<<case "coffee">>
			The coffee arrives promptly, served with a light drizzle of creamer.
			<<if $robin.stayup is 2>>
				<<set $robin.stayup to 1>>
				Robin doesn't even wait for it to cool down. <<He>> downs the coffee like <<he>>'d been trapped in a desert the past week. "God, I really needed that.<<if $phase2 isnot 7>> Thank you.<</if>>" <<He>> sighs contentedly.
			<<else>>
				<<set $robin.stayup to 0>>
				"There's some schoolwork I need to get caught up on, so I could use the pick-me-up." <<He>> raises the cup. "Cheers."
			<</if>>
		<<case "fruity ale" "shandy" "autumn ale" "winter ale">>
			A tall glass of $phase arrives quickly.
			<<if _robin.trauma gte 60>>
				<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("bad_day_drinking")>>
				Robin immediately takes a big gulp. <<He>> winces, then sets the glass down and coughs. "That's—" <<He>> coughs again. "That's strong..."
				<br><br>

				Despite that, <<he>> takes yet another gulp. Gwylan looks concerned. "Slow down, dear. You should really only drink to make a good day better, and no offense, but you don't seem to be having a good day."
				<br><br>

				"Huh? No, no, I'm having a lovely time. I'm here with my two best buddies. Life is great," Robin says. Gwylan smiles, but you see the concern in <<person1>><<his>> eyes.
			<<else>>
				Robin looks a little nervous as <<he>> inspects it. "I don't normally drink. This seems like a lot.
				<<switch $phase>>
					<<case "fruity ale" "shandy">>I do like fruit, though."
					<<case "autumn ale">>The colour reminds me of autumn, though."
					<<case "winter ale">>But hey, it looks festive!"
				<</switch>>
				<<He>> takes a sip. Immediately, <<his>> face scrunches up and <<he>> shakes <<his>> head. "Oh, that's strong." <<He>> takes a deep breath.
				<br><br>

				Gwylan watches in amusement. "You get used to it, and then you'll come to love it I guarantee you."
			<</if>>
		<<case "fruit salad">>
			After a brief moment, the salad arrives. <span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "gingerbread">>
			<<if $rng is 100>>
				A gingerbread man arrives promptly. Or rather, the <<person3>><<person>> arrives promptly with a gingerbread man on a plate.
			<<else>>
				The gingerbread arrives promptly. It's shaped like a little <<print either("man", "woman", "house", "dog", "cat", "cow")>>, and tastefully decorated with frosting.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			"They're so fun, these little shapes people make gingerbread into. Imagine if we did that with other food?" Robin giggles. "I'd be all for it.<<if $christmas and Time.monthDay is 25>> Merry Christmas!<</if>>"
		<<case "pancakes">>
			The pancakes arrive promptly, drenched in strawberry jam.
			<br><br>

			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "crepes">>
			The crepes soon arrive after a short wait.
			<br><br>

			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "deluxe cream bun">>
			<<set _gwylanKnows to $gwylanSeen.includes("cafe_chef_truth") or $chef_speech is "truth">><<set _face to $player.bodyliquid.face>><<set _mouth to $player.bodyliquid.mouth>>
			<<if _gwylanKnows>>Gwylan smirks at you. <</if>>The cream bun arrives after a few minutes, hot and ready, and packed with delicious creamy filling. Robin rubs <<his>> hands together as the food appears.
			<<if $chef_state>>
				"These look even better in person! It's a shame the price <<if $bun_value is 15000>>is through the roof<<else>>is so high<</if>>, or else I'd be eating them every day.<<if $phase2 isnot 7>> Thank you so much for getting me one!<</if>>"
			<<else>>
				"These always looked so good, but the price makes it hard to justify.<<if $phase2 isnot 7>> Thank you for getting me one!<</if>>"
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<He>> lifts it up with both hands, closes <<his>> eyes, and takes a big, slow bite. When <<he>> lowers the bun, you realise that
			<<if $chef_state>>
				<span class="lewd"><<his>> entire lower face has been covered in cream</span>. <<arousal 600>><<garousal>>
			<<else>>
				<<his>> entire lower face has been covered in cream.
			<</if>>
			<br><br>

			<<if $chef_state>>
				You <<if _gwylanKnows>>and Gwylan <</if>>blush, trying to hold back laughter. Robin opens <<his>> eyes and looks at you befuzzled. "What? What's so funny?" <<He>> licks <<his>> mouth.
				<br><br>

				<<if _gwylanKnows>>
					You stare at Gwylan. <<person1>><<He>> stares back at you. It's too much. You both start giggling uncontrollably. It wasn't even that funny, but you're spurred on by each other's amusement.
					<br><br>

					Robin pouts. "Come on, tell me!" You struggle to create the words. All that comes out is a wheeze. You weakly point to <<person2>><<his>> mouth. "Oh! How clumsy..." Robin says, and tries to wipe it away. Instead, <<he>> just ends up <span class="lewd">smearing it out even more</span>. <<arousal 800>><<garousal>>
					<br><br>

					You clutch your stomach as tears well up in your eyes, pleading with Gwylan to please do something. <<pain 1>><<gpain>>
					<br><br>

					<<person1>><<He>> musters up the strength to produce a handkerchief from one of <<his>> pockets. <<He>> simply holds it out to Robin, who takes it and wipes the cream off. It takes several more minutes for you and Gwylan to sufficiently calm down. <<trauma -3>><<ltrauma>>

					<<if _face.goo + _face.semen + _face.nectar + _mouth.goo + _mouth.semen + _mouth.nectar gte 1>>
						<br><br>
						You were so focused on Robin's face that you had entirely forgotten your own face is just as messy. You feel pretty silly.
					<</if>>
				<<else>>
					Gwylan raises an eyebrow at you. "Indeed I wonder the same. Care to tell us, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "my">>?" <<person1>><<he>> teases.
					<br><br>

					You point a finger at Robin's mouth. Gwylan shakes <<his>> head and produces a handkerchief. "It's just a little cream, silly <<girl>>." <<He>> wipes it off, and you soon come to your senses again.

					<<if _face.goo + _face.semen + _face.nectar + _mouth.goo + _mouth.semen + _mouth.nectar gte 1>>
						<br><br>
						You were so focused on Robin's face that you had entirely forgotten your own face is just as messy. You feel pretty silly.
					<</if>>
				<</if>>
			<<else>>
				"Let me take care of that, dear," Gwylan says, and pulls out a handkerchief. <<person1>><<He>> wipes Robin's cheeks and nose with it. "Those cream buns always get so messy. They're tasty of course, but I prefer to eat them with a knife and fork personally."

				<<if _face.goo + _face.semen + _face.nectar + _mouth.goo + _mouth.semen + _mouth.nectar gte 1>>
					<br><br>
					Once Robin's face is clean, <<he>> moves the handkerchief to yours. You had entirely forgotten about the gunk on yours, but it's wiped off just as quick. "There we are, two pretty little faces, all clean!" <<He>> boops both of you on the nose.
					<<bodyliquid "face" "all" -10>><<bodyliquid "mouth" "all" -2>>
				<</if>>
			<</if>>
		<<default>>
			The order arrives quickly. Robin looks surprised. "I didn't even know this was on the menu?" You shrug. "Must be one of those 'secret' menu items."
			<br><br>

			<<He>> digs in, and the rumbling hunger in <<his>> stomach soon subsides.
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	The three of you make some small talk as Robin finishes up.
<<elseif $phase2 is 3 or $phase2 is 6>> /* Share */
	You slide your $phase over to Robin.
	<<if $phase2 is 3>> /* Robin did nothing */
		"Here. I'm full, so you can have the rest."
		<br><br>

		"Really? Are you sure?" <<he>> asks. You assure <<him>> it's fine. <<He>> hugs you. "Thank you! You're a great <<friend>>."
	<<else>> /* Robin tried to order */
		"Save the money. I won't be finishing mine anyway, so it's yours if you want it."
		<br><br>

		<<He>> smiles. "Thank you! A small portion is actually plenty enough for me," <<he>> says.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	<<switch $phase>>
		<<case "coffee">>
			<<if $robin.stayup is 2>>
				<<set $robin.stayup to 1>>
				<<He>> downs the remainder of the coffee like <<he>>'d been trapped in a desert the past week. "God, I really needed that. Thank you." <<He>> sighs contentedly.
			<<else>>
				<<set $robin.stayup to 0>>
				"There's some schoolwork I need to get caught up on, so I could use the pick-me-up." <<He>> raises the cup. "Cheers."
			<</if>>
		<<case "fruity ale" "shandy" "autumn ale" "winter ale">>
			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "fruit salad">>
			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "gingerbread">>
			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "pancakes">>
			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "crepes">>
			<span class="red">TODO: Robin</span>
		<<case "deluxe cream bun">>
			<<He>> devours the remainder of the bun in almost record time.
		<<default>>
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	The three of you make some small talk as Robin finishes up.
<<elseif $phase2 is 4>> /* Discourage */
	<<set _success to (_robin.love + _robin.trauma - _robin.dom) gte random(20, 90)>>
	You glance at Robin with disapproval. <<He>> freezes up as <<he>> seems to sense your gaze.
	<br><br>

	You cross your arms.
	<<if $robinpaid is 1>>
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"L-look, Robin. I understand that I'm paying for you and all, but your money's supposed to help ease that burden on me..." you admit.
			<<case "bratty">>
				"What do you think you're doing, huh? I work my ass off to support us both and yet here you are, throwing your money around without a care," you roar.
			<<default>>
				"It doesn't seem very fair that I'm paying for you, only for you to splurge on overpriced food. We need every penny we can get, you know," you sneer.
		<</switch>>
	<<elseif $robindebtknown is 1>>
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"Um... pardon me, but don't you have a debt to cover too? I doubt Bailey's going to let you off easy if you're spending money at the cafe," you say.
			<<case "bratty">>
				"Robin, you fool. Did you never even consider that you still have a debt to pay off? Bailey's gonna be pissed if <<nnpc_he "Bailey">> finds out you spent it all here," you say.
			<<default>>
				"You're barely breaking even as it stands! Think, Robin. Do you really want to face Bailey's punishments again?" you say.
		<</switch>>
	<<else>>
		<<switch $speech_attitude>>
			<<case "meek">>
				"Robin, are you... are you sure you want to do that? The food here, it's not very... healthy," you say.
			<<case "bratty">>
				"Save your breath. This food is overpriced junk, you're better off just eating the food at <<if Time.schoolDay>>school<<else>>home<</if>>," you say.
			<<default>>
				"Hey, Robin, that's a lot of money for just some $phase. I really don't think it's worth it," you say.
		<</switch>>
	<</if>>
	<br><br>

	Robin turns to you.
	<<if _success>>
		<<He>> tries to say something, but stops <<himself>>, and lowers <<his>> head sheepishly. "<span class="green">Yeah, you're right...</span>" <<he>> sighs. "I just thought... nevermind."
		<br><br>

		The <<person3>><<person>> arrives. "Yes, did you need anything?" Robin shakes <<person2>><<his>> head. "No, sorry, it was nothing." The <<person3>><<personsimple>> rolls <<his>> eyes and walks away.
	<<else>>
		<<switch $phase>>
			<<case "coffee">><<set $robinmoney -= 2>>
			<<case "fruit salad">><<set $robinmoney -= 5>>
			<<case "gingerbread">><<set $robinmoney -= 6>>
			<<case "fruity ale" "shandy", "autumn ale", "winter ale">><<set $robinmoney -= 7>>
			<<case "pancakes" "crepes">><<set $robinmoney -= 10>>
			<<case "deluxe cream bun">><<set $robinmoney -= 50>>
			<<default>><span class="red">Error: Could not find $phase among the list of accepted food items. Please report.</span>
		<</switch>>
		<<His>> nose scrunches a bit. "<span class="red">But you're having $phase?</span>
		<<if $robinpaid>>
