:: Gwylan Ocean Breeze Kiss
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is 0>>
	You lean forwards and kiss Gwylan. <<Hes>> surprised by your bold display, but smiles against your lips before kissing back. You only break apart to breathe. <<gwylanKiss>><<takeKissVirginity "Gwylan" `(isLoveInterest("Gwylan") ? "loveInterest" : "romantic")`>>
	<br><br>
	<<if $robinromance is 1>>
		You snap out of it upon hearing a guttural noise and a rustle. You turn to see Robin's chair fallen over and the balcony door swinging back and forth. Robin <<himself>> is nowhere to be seen.<<npcincr Robin love -5>><<lllove "Robin">>
		<br><br>

		Gwylan bites <<person1>><<his>> lip. "I think you may have upset the <<person2>><<personsimple>>," <<person1>><<he>> says.
		<br><br>

		<<He>> pauses, and then flicks you on the nose. "Naughty <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "simple">>. You knew this would happen, didn't you? Let's hope for your own sake <<person2>><<hes>> the forgiving sort."
		<<unset $daily.robin_in_cafe>><<if $robin.timer.hurt is 0>><<set $robin.hurtReason to "you kissing Gwylan">><<set $robin.timer.hurt to 1>><</if>>
		<<endevent>><<npc Gwylan>><<person1>>
	<<else>>
