	<br><br>

	<<He>> melts in your embrace, savouring the feel of your lips on <<hers>>. <<npcincr Robin love 1>><<npcincr Robin lust 5>><<glove "Robin">><<glust "Robin">>
	<br><br>
	You think you see irritation on Gwylan's face from the corner of your eye, but <<person1>><<hes>> smiling when you pull apart. "Looks like I still have things to learn," <<person1>><<he>> says, giving Robin a pointed look before returning <<his>> gaze to you. "You should teach me that technique sometime, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> turns <<his>> gaze to Robin, then back at you, and giggles. "If you can convince your <<person2>><<if $robinromance is 1>><<personsimple>><</if>>friend, that is." Robin frowns, as if unsure what Gwylan means.
<<else>>
	You choose to keep watching the couple. That kiss must have really fired them up, as they start fervorously groping at each other's bodies.
	<br><br>

	One of them suddenly tackles the other into the water like a wild beast in heat. Neither show a care in the world as the waves wash over them.
	<br><br>

	It's hard to see what they're doing at this point as they're both almost completely submerged, <<if $awareness gte 400>>but you have a pretty good idea, and it puts a big blush on your face. <<arousal 1000>><<ggarousal>><<elseif $awareness gte 0>>but it's clearly very lewd. You blush. <<arousal 600>><<garousal>><<else>>but it looks quite uncomfortable.<</if>>
	<br><br>

	Robin already looked away a long time ago, but Gwylan is still leaning over the railing in fascination. <<npcincr Robin lust 2>><<npcincr Gwylan lust 5>><<glust "Robin">><<glust "Gwylan">>
<</if>>
<br><br>

