:: Gwylan Talk Struggles Spite
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylan.triumph to "spite">>
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"I-I think everyone's out to get me," you say. "I don't... I don't want to let them win."
	<<case "bratty">>
		"Everyone is determined to knock me down," you say. "I'm determined to not give them the satisfaction of seeing me broken."
	<<default>>
		"It feels like everyone wants to hurt me," you say. "And I don't want to let them win."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan smiles sadly. "Well, I hope you know you're not alone in this fight of yours. I'll always be in your corner. If..." <<He>> pauses, trying to sort out <<his>> words.
"If you ever stopped visiting, I'd miss our conversations. <span class="pink">I'd miss you.</span>"
<br><br>

<<link [[Say nothing|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Say you'd miss Gwylan too|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 2>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Talk Struggles Survival
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylan.triumph to "survival">>
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"What other choice do I have? If I stop, I'll just fade away," you say.
	<<case "bratty">>
		"It's not like I can just fall over and give up," you say.
	<<default>>
		"Survival is the only motivation I need," you say. "Everything else is secondary."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan thinks for a moment, before slowly nodding. "Many people think they'll be able to hold on through anything, but few are able to push through with sheer willpower alone.
Eventually, something will break. The world won't make sense anymore, your head won't work right, your legs simply won't move no matter how hard you try.
You must be very strong if that's all that's been pushing you on."
<br><br>

<<He>> cautiously smiles, and seems to be trying to sort <<his>> words.
"Please be careful, and find something else to hold on for. If you ever stopped coming around, I'd miss our conversations. <span class="pink">I'd miss you.</span>"
<br><br>

<<link [[Say nothing|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Say you'd miss Gwylan too|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 2>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Talk Struggles Optimism
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylan.triumph to "optimism">>
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"This too shall pass," you say. "All things do. I just have to keep my eyes forward, and I'll find a better future."
	<<case "bratty">>
		"There's a light at the end of this tunnel," you say. "A brighter future. I have to reach it, and to do that, I have to keep walking. If I can't walk, I'll crawl."
	<<default>>
		"Not every day will be rainy," you say. "I can make a better future. I know I can."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan stares at you, <<his>> head tilted and <<his>> mouth slightly open. <<He>> then giggles. "Incredible that you can say that after everything you've told me. You're strong, but still a little naive."
<<He>> smiles. "Hold onto that. It's precious, and refreshing."
<br><br>

<<His>> smile slowly fades. "Take care not to break when that optimism crashes down. If you ever stopped coming around, I'd miss our conversations. <span class="pink">I'd miss you.</span>"
<br><br>

<<link [[Say nothing|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 1>><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Say you'd miss Gwylan too|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 2>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>>
