:: Gwylan Talk Struggles Orphans
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $gwylan.triumph to "orphans">>
<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>
		"I have to be strong for the other orphans," you say. "They're the closest thing I have to a family."
	<<case "bratty">>
		"I need to be there for the other orphans," you say sternly. "Enough of us get broken every week."
	<<default>>
		"The other orphans need me," you say. "They're the closest thing I have to family."
<</switch>>
<br><br>

Gwylan smiles. "That's awfully noble of you. I'm not surprised. I knew you had a good heart when I first saw you, and you know your place in the world well. I'm glad they have someone as strong as you to look out for them."
<br><br>

<<He>> returns <<his>> gaze to the ocean. "I had people to stick around for, too. People I couldn't leave behind. Not many left, though."
<br><br>

After a moment, <<he>> turns back to you. "Stay strong for them, and for me. If you ever stopped coming around, I'd miss our conversations. <span class="pink">I'd miss you.</span>"
<<He>> pauses, <<his>> eyes closed, before saying softly, "Would you miss me, too, were I to disappear?"
<br><br>

<<link [[Yes|Gwylan Talk Struggles 2]]>><<set $phase to 2>><<npcincr Gwylan dom 1>><</link>>
