	<<elseif $daily.robin_in_cafe>>
		<<getouticon>><<link [[Meet with Robin inside (0:01)|Gwylan Talk Struggles Meet Robin]]>><<pass 1>><<set $phase to 1>><<endevent "phaseless">><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><</link>>
	<<else>>
		<<getouticon>><<link [[Go back inside (0:01)|Ocean Breeze]]>><<pass 1>><<endevent>><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><</link>>
	<</if>>
<<else>>
	<<getouticon>><<link [[Leave (0:01)|Cliff Street]]>><<pass 1>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><<unset $cafe_study>><<storeon "cafe_balcony">><</link>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Talk Struggles Meet Robin
<<effects>><<npc Robin>><<person1>>

<<if $phase is 0>>
	<<set $outside to 1>>
	You spot Robin <<if Weather.precipitation is "rain">>under an awning<<else>>next to a streetlight<</if>>. <<He>> looks a little confused when you approach.
	<br><br>

	"Where's Gwylan?" <<he>> asks. "Is <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> not coming with us?"
	<br><br>

	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"S-sorry, <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> told me <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> needed some time alone," you explain.
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Yeah, apparently not. <<nnpc_He "Gwylan">> got all mysterious and asked to be left alone," you say, shrugging.
		<<default>>
			"It would appear so. I think <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> just wanted some space," you say.
	<</switch>>
	Robin looks a little worried, so you assure <<him>> that Gwylan's not upset with any of you.
	<br><br>

	"Okay, well... you'll still walk with me though, right?" <<he>> asks.
	<br><br>

	<<schoolicon "building">><<link [[Walk to school (0:10)|Gwylan Walk School Robin]]>><<pass 1>><<set $phase to 2>><</link>>
	<br>
	<<clifficon>><<link [[Make an excuse and leave (0:01)|Cliff Street]]>><<pass 1>><<endevent>><</link>>
<<else>>
	You spot Robin by the counter. <<He>> looks to be waiting eagerly for <<his>> order.
	<br><br>

	<<He>> notices you as you approach. "Hey, what's up? You gonna order something too?"
	<br><br>

	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"Actually... Gwylan told me <<nnpc_he "Gwylan">> needed some time alone," you admit.
		<<case "bratty">>
			"Nope. Gwylan got all mysterious and asked to be left alone," you say, shrugging.
		<<default>>
			"No, but, I think Gwylan wants some space right now," you say.
	<</switch>>
	Robin looks a little worried, so you assure <<him>> that Gwylan's not upset with any of you.
	<br><br>

	"Sticky toffee pudding!" a voice calls out. "Here!" Robin replies. "Actually, could you put that in a bag for me? I'd like it to-go."
	<br><br>

	<<He>> turns back to you. "I guess I'll be heading back home then," <<he>> says with a hint of disappointment. But <<he>> perks up upon receiving <<his>> order. "Still, free dessert!"
	<br><br>

	<<link [[Next|Ocean Breeze]]>><<endevent>><</link>>
<</if>>

:: Gwylan Chef Cream
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is 1 or $phase is 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("cafe_chef_truth")>>
	<<if $phase is 2 and $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1 and !$willpowerSuccess>>
		You try to keep yourself quiet. <span class="red">You feel scolding disappointment wash over you, despite Gwylan's continued smile.</span>
		You can't help it. <span class="red">You tell <<him>> everything.</span> <<stress 6>><<gstress>>
	<<else>>
