<<else>>
	<<if $hypnosis_traits.devotion gte 1>>
		<span class="green">You block out the compulsion.</span>
	<</if>>
	<<switch $speech_attitude>>
		<<case "meek">>
			"I-I can't tell," you say. "It's a secret recipe."
		<<case "bratty">>
			"I'm not giving my secret recipe away for anyone," you say, crossing your arms. "It's nothing personal."
		<<default>>
			"You're right, it's a secret. I can't reveal it," you say.
	<</switch>>
	<br><br>

	Gwylan pouts. "Very well. I'll squeeze it out of you one day." <<He>> brushes your shoulder as <<he>> walks by. <<His>> choice of words makes you wonder if <<he>> already knows, and just wanted to hear you say it.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Cliff Street]]>><<endevent>><<set $eventskip to 1>><</link>>
