:: Gwylan Talk TF Revealed Confront
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You remember what you saw. The tail. <<His>> teeth. Those ears on <<his>> hat. It might have been nothing, but what if it wasn't?
<br><br>

"I always wondered why you wear that big witch hat, with the ears. Are you hiding something?" You reach up for Gwylan's head.
