<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning")>>
	<<He>> crosses <<his>> arms and looks away. "Do you understand, now? Do you understand why I can't let us become... more?" <<He>> points to <<his>> ears.
	"Every instinct in my body tells me to find a mate for life, something I can't have. Something you and I can't be."

	<<if $transformationParts.traits.mateForLife isnot "disabled">>
