<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You keep staring.
<br><br>

"Are you quite done? I have customers to attend to," <<he>> says. The shop is completely empty save for the two of you, as usual.
<br><br>

<<switch $speech_attitude>>
	<<case "meek">>"Th-they're cute," you say.
