:: Gwylan Yearning Letter
<<effects>>
You approach the window. There's a crow pecking at the glass. <span class="purple">It's looking right at you.</span>
<br><br>

There's something tied around its neck. You look closer. It's a piece of paper, <span class="purple">and it has your name on it</span>.
