:: Gwylan Yearning Letter 2
<<effects>>
<span class="narration">
Hello, dear.
<br><br>

I'm sending my sincerest apology for snapping at you and kicking you out of the shop. I won't invent any justifications for my outburst.
I've reflected over these passing days, and the simple truth is that it's boring around here without you to tell me your stories.
I don't have many friends, and you are a dear one to me.
<br><br>

I miss you, is what I'm saying.
<<if $gwylan.scratchDoor gte 3>>
	All your scratching at the shop's door didn't help.
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning_pub")>>
	I'm also sorry about what happened at the pub.
	<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("yearning_pub_kiss")>>
		It was irresponsible of me, and I've gone and made everything more complicated now.
	<<else>>
		In case it wasn't obvious, you leaving me there was actually the last thing I wanted. I'm sorry for pushing you away like that.
	<</if>>
	<br><br>
<</if>>

If you find it in your heart to forgive me, come by the shop soon. If not, please come by anyways. There's something important I wish to discuss, and it's urgent.
<br><br>

Still here,<br>
<<ind>>~ Gwylan
</span>
<br><br>

The crow caws at you again as you finish reading.
