	<br><br>

	A third stands beside them. It wears a black tunic with a white cross, as well as an emotionless white mask. It points to its left.
	You follow its arm, and find a dark doorway leading to a staircase. You see a faint light at the top.
<<else>>
	You try avoiding the sound, but it seems to be following you. You can only hear it when you have a distinct way forward, though.
	As if it's guiding you by its lack of presence.
