<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<set $location to "promenade">>
You end up on Starfish Street. Gwylan walks you onto the promenade.
<br><br>

It's not too crowded, but there's many couples walking side by side. After a moment, Gwylan takes your arm and walks closer to you. "We should blend in," <<he>> says hastily.
<br><br>

You occasionally stop to peruse some of the stores. The two of you laugh as you point out obvious bootleg merchandise. <<He>> stops laughing at the next store, and stares intently at something on the wall.
<<if _gwylanTF.known>>
	<<His>> tail sways back and forth rapidly.
<</if>>
<br><br>

You follow <<his>> gaze. There's a huge fox plushie hanging up. Its tail is almost as large as the rest of it.
<br><br>

<<if $money gte 3000>>
	<<icon "fox_plushie.png">><<link [[Buy it for Gwylan (£30)|Gwylan Promenade Walk Fox Plushie]]>><<set $phase to "gwylan">><<money -3000 "shopping">><<set $yearningScore++>><</link>><<gyearning true>>
	<br>
	<<icon "fox_plushie.png">><<link [[Buy it for yourself (£30)|Gwylan Promenade Walk Fox Plushie]]>><<set $phase to "self">><<money -3000 "shopping">><</link>>
<<else>>
	<span class="blue">You can't afford it.</span>
<</if>>
<br>
<<getouticon>><<link [[Keep walking|Gwylan Promenade Walk Sea]]>><<pass 10>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Promenade Walk Fox Plushie
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You hand out the money to the vendor. Gwylan doesn't notice until the plushie is taken down and handed to you.
<br><br>

<<if $phase is "gwylan">>
	<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("fox_plushie_gwylan")>>
	You then hand it to <<him>>. <<He>> blinks at you, and cautiously takes it. "Oh, dear, I wasn't staring at it because I wanted it!" <<He>> giggles. "But thank you. I'll cherish it."
	<<He>> thinks for a moment, before handing £30 to the vendor <<himself>>. A second fox plushie is handed through the window, which <<he>> then hands to you.
	<br><br>

	"You'll need something to remember this moment." <<He>> pets the tail. "Ah, it's a pillow! My bed will be inescapable at this rate."
<<else>>
	<<He>> smiles at you. "Good choice. You'll need something to remember this moment." <<He>> pets the tail. "Ah, it's a pillow! I hope it brings you restful sleep."
<</if>>
<br><br>

<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("fox_plushie")>>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Promenade Walk Sea]]>><<pass 10>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Promenade Walk Sea
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
You stop by a railing, and watch the sea together for some time. <<stress -3>><<lstress>>
<br><br>

"Are you having fun?" <<he>> asks. "The true mark of connection is taking joy in doing nothing in particular, so long as it's with a dear friend."
<br><br>

<<He>> stays silent for a while after that, <<his>> smile slowly fading. <<He>> looks to <<his>> side. "Over there." <<He>> takes your hand and leads you over to a bench.
<br><br>

<<He>> motions for you to sit down first, and sits right next to you.
<<if $gwylanSeen.includes("fox_plushie_gwylan")>>
	There's enough room on the bench for both of your massive fox plushies, too.
<<elseif $gwylanSeen.includes("fox_plushie")>>
	There's enough room on the bench for your massive fox plushie, too.
<</if>>
Gwylan rests <<his>> head on your shoulder. You think you hear <<him>> let out a sigh of contentment.
<br><br>

<<link [[Pull <<him>> closer|Gwylan Promenade Walk Chat]]>><<set $phase to "pull">><<set $yearningScore++>><</link>><<gyearning true>>
<br>
<<link [[Sit still|Gwylan Promenade Walk Chat]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Promenade Walk Chat
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>
<<if $phase is "pull">>
	You put your arm around Gwylan and pull <<him>> closer. <<He>> looks surprised, but leans into it.
	<br><br>
<</if>>

"Forgive me for how abrupt this all was, <<pcpetname "Gwylan" "name">>. I..." <<He>> pauses, and shakes <<his>> head.
<br><br>

"I wanted to... play pretend." <<He>> looks up at you. "To pretend that you and I could be something more. Your kiss poisoned my mind. After what you said, I still couldn't stop thinking about it.
<<if $gwylan.yearnResponse is "important">>
	You told me it was important to you. You kept coming around, kept trying to break this wall I've put up. I felt so selfish."
<<elseif $gwylan.yearnResponse is "nothing">>
	You told me it meant nothing, but then you kept coming back. You kept trying to chip away at this wall between us."
<<else>>
	You keep coming back, and you keep chipping away at this wall between us."
<</if>>
<<He>> hugs you tighter, before pulling away.
<br><br>

"Despite my best efforts, you're stuck in my head. No amount of me trying to push you away will change that, now. So, I suppose I owe you my true feelings."
<br><br>

<<He>> doesn't continue at first. <<He>> seems to be trying to find the right words. Finally, <<he>> speaks.
"Do you want to know how I really feel? You know I like collecting things. Clothes. Knick-knacks." A pause. "Memories."
<br><br>

Another pause.
<br><br>

<<link [[Next|Gwylan Promenade Walk Chat 2]]>><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Promenade Walk Chat 2
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

"Everything in my shop has a purpose, even if I don't always remember. If I stare long enough, I will, though." <<Hes>> staring at you, now.
"You're like that. A treasure. I want to hold you close and keep you. But that isn't love, and I can't rob you of your freedom like that. I meant it when I said that you're not ready for forever, but I was half wrong.
I'm the one who's not ready for it, and I never was. You're a treasure I can't have." <<His>> hand squeezes yours. "<span class="purple">My heart can't love anymore.</span> Not truly. You're my treasure, but I can't love you."
<br><br>

<<if $auriga_scar>>
	<<He>> frowns. "Besides, your heart is already wounded, much like my own. Together, that would spell disaster."
	<br><br>
<<elseif $templePromised isnot "">>
	<<He>> frowns, looking at your promise ring. "You wear a ring of binding on your finger. You're already breaking a promise. Would you do the same to me?"
	<br><br>
<</if>>

The silence that passes is agonising. The sea attacks the shore like a hungry predator. You sit and listen until you hear <<his>> voice again.
<br><br>

"<span class="green">But maybe it doesn't have to be forever.</span> Maybe we'll both hurt more if I keep being so thorny. Maybe I just need to..." <<He>> stops <<himself>> yet again, and chuckles dryly.
<br><br>

<<link [["\"Stop and smell the roses.\""|Gwylan Promenade Walk Love Interest]]>><<set $phase to "roses">><</link>>
<br>
<<link [["\"Speak the sea.\""|Gwylan Promenade Walk Love Interest]]>><<set $phase to "sea">><</link>>
<br>
<<link [["\"Share the burden with someone.\""|Gwylan Promenade Walk Love Interest]]>><<set $phase to "burden">><</link>>
<br>
<<link [[Say nothing|Gwylan Promenade Walk Love Interest]]>><<set $phase to "silent">><</link>>
<br>

:: Gwylan Promenade Walk Love Interest
<<effects>><<run statusCheck("Gwylan")>>

<<if $phase is "roses">>
	"Stop and smell the roses," you finish. <<He>> smiles. "Exactly."
<<elseif $phase is "sea">>
	"Speak the sea." <<His>> eyes widen. You're not sure why you said that. The words just happened.
<<elseif $phase is "burden">>
	"Share the burden with someone," you say. "With me." <<He>> looks sad for a moment. No, not sad. Nostalgic.
<<else>>
	You don't say anything. You don't need to. You both already know.
<</if>>
<br><br>

Without warning, <span class="lewd"><<he>> pulls you into a kiss</span>.
<br><br>

<<gwylanKiss>>
<br><br>

<<He>> pulls away. "What we have can't be love. But that doesn't mean we can't still enjoy it, with what time we do have together. We'll both be hurt some day, when this little affair of ours slips away. But let's just enjoy it for now. Not forever. Just for now."
<br><br>

<<He>> hugs you once more. "You're worth the hurt, because you've shared so much of that hurt with me already. If I don't want it to end, then I only need to stop trying to push you away."
<br><br>

<<He>> stands, and pulls you up, too. <<He>> braces <<himself>>. "If my heart could sing for anyone, my dear, it would be for you." <<He>> gives you another peck on the lips, and the two of you begin the walk back to the forest shop.
<br><br>

<<set $gwylanSeen.pushUnique("partners")>>
<<loveInterestAdd "Gwylan">>
<br><br>

<<if $yearningScore gt 0>>
	<<npcincr Gwylan dom $yearningScore>>
<</if>>
<<unset $yearningScore>>
<<link [[Next|Forest Shop Entrance]]>><<endevent>><<pass 10>><</link>>
<br>
